hadiths[235]{hadithnumber,text}:
3370,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah key nazdik dua sey ziyada moazziz aur mukarram koi chiz (ibadat) nahin hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey marfoo sirf Imran Qattaan ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Imran Al Qattaan ye ibne Dawer hain aur un ki kunniyat Abul-Awaam hai."
3371,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''dua ibadat ka maghz (hasil aur nichod) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf ibne-Lahiyaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3372,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''dua hi ibadat hai, phir aap ney aayat : (وقال ربكم ادعوني أستجب لكم إن الذين يستكبرون an عبادتي سيدخلون جهنم داخرين) ''tumhara Rab farmata hai, tum mujhey pukaro , main tumhari pukar (dua) ko qubul karunga, jo log mujh sey maangney sey ghamand kartey hain, wo jahannam mein zaleel aur khuwar ho kar dakhil hongey'' (Al Momin-60) padhi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Mansoor ney ye hadees Aamash sey aur Aamash ney Zar sey riwayat ki hai, hum isey sirf Zar ki riwayat sey jantey hain, ye Zar bin Abdullah Hamdaani hain Suqa (bharosemand) hain, umr bin Zar key walid hain."""
3373,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Allah sey sawal nahin karta padhi. Allah us sey naraz aur naakhush hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Wakee aur kaee raawiyon ney ye hadees Abul-Maleeh sey riwayat ki hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, Abul-Maleeh ka naam Sabeeh hai, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko aisa hi kehtey huye suna hai, unhoney kaha ke unhen Faarsi bhi kaha jata hai."
3374,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik ghazwe mein they jab hum lotey aur hamein Madina dikhai deney laga to logon ney takbir kahi aur buland aawaz sey takbir kahi. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumhara Rab behra nahin hai aur na hi wo ghaaieb aur ghair hazir hai, wo tumharey darmiyan mojud hai, wo tumharey kajawon aur sawaariyon key darmiyan (yani bahut qarib) hai phir aap ney farmaya : ''Abdullah bin Qais ! kya main tumhen jannat key khazanon mein sey eik khazana na bataaun? (لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله) (jannat key khazanon mein sey eik khazana hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Abu-Usman Nahdi ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Mil hai aur Sa'di ka naam Amr bin Esa hai."
3375,"eik aadmi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Islam key ehkam aur qawanin (qaanun) to merey liye bahut hain, kuchh thodi si cheezen mujhey bata dijiye jin par mein (mazbooti) sey jama rahun, aap ney farmaya : ''tumhari zaban har waqt Allah ki yad aur zikr sey tar rahey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3376,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : qiyamat key din Allah key nazdik darje key lihaz sey kon sey bandey sab sey afzal aur sab sey unchey martabe waley hongey? aap ney farmaya : ''kasrat sey Allah ka zikr karney waley mard aur kasrat sey Allah ka zikr karney wali aurten.'' mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki raah mein ladaai ladney waley (ghaazi) sey bhi badh kar? aap ney farmaya : ''(haan) agar-che usney apni talwaar sey kuffar aur mushrekin ko maara ho, aur itni shadeed jang ladi ho ke uski talwaar toot gaee ho, aur wo khud khoon sey rang gaya ho, tab bhi Allah ka zikr karney waley us sey darjey mein badhey huye hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Daraaj ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3377,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya main tumharey sab sey behtar aur tumharey Rab key nazdik sab sey pakizah aur sab sey buland darjey waley amal ki tumhen khabar na dun? wo amal tumharey liye sona chaandi kharch karney sey behtar hai, wo amal tumharey liye us sey bhi behtar hai ke tum (maidane jang mein) apney dushman sey takraao, wo tumhari gardanen kaatey aur tum un ki (yani tumharey jihad karney sey bhi afzal)'' logon ney kaha : ji haan, (zarur bataiye) aap ney farmaya : ''wo Allah Taala ka zikr hai.''  Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Allah key zikr sey badh kar Allah key azab sey bachaney wali koi aur chiz nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : baaz ney ye hadees Abdullah bin Saeed isi tarah isi sanad sey riwayat ki hai, aur baa'zon ney isey un sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai."
3378,"unhoney gawahi di ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo qom Allah ko yad karti hai (zikre Ilaahi mein rehti hai) usey farishtey gher letey hain aur rehmate Ilaahi usey dhanp leti hai, is par sakeenat nazil hoti hai aur Allah uska zikr apney yhaan farishton mein karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3379,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) masjid gaey (wahan bethey huye logon sey) puchha : tum log kis liye bethey ho? un logon ney kaha : hum yahan beth kar Allah ko yad kartey hain, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya ! qism Allah ki ! tum ko usi chiz ney yahan bitha rakha hai? unhoney kaha : qism Allah ki, hum isi maqsad sey yahan bethey hain, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey tum logon par kisi tohmat ki bina par qism nahin khilaai hai padhi. , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas merey jaisa maqam aur manzilat rakhney wala koi shakhs mujh sey kam (adab aur ehtiyat key sabab) aap sey hadisein bayan karney wala nahin hai. (phir bhi main tumhen ye hadees suna raha hun) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney Sahaba key paas gaey wo sab daayra laga kar bethey huye they, un sey kaha : kis liye bethey ho? unhoney kaha : hum yahan beth kar Allah ka zikr kartey hain, Allah ney hamein Islam ki taraf jo hidayat di hai, aur musalman bana kar hum par jo ehsan farmaya hai hum is par uska shukriya ada kartey hain, aur uski hamd bayan kartey hain, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya waqaee? ! qism hai tumhen isi chiz ney yahan bitha rakha hai?'' unhoney kaha : qism Allah ki, hamein isi maqsad ney yahan bithaya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''main ney tumhen qism isliye nahin dilai hai, mainey tum logon par kisi tohmat ki bina par qism nahin khilaai hai, baat ye hai ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) merey paas aaye aur unhoney mujhey bataya aur khabar di ke Allah Taala tumharey zariye farishton par fakhr karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3380,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log kisi majlis mein bethein aur Allah ki yad na karen, aur na apney Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par (durood) bhejein to ye chiz unkey liye hasrat aur nadaamat ka baais bin sakti hai. Allah chahey to unhen azab dey , aur chahey to unhen bakhsh dey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- aur aap key qol « ترة » key maana hain hasrat aur nadaamat key , baaz arbi-daan hazraat kehtey hain : « ترة » key maana badle key hain."
3381,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jo koi banda Allah sey dua kar key maangta hai Allah usey ya to uski maangi hui chiz dey deta hai, ya us dua key nateeje mein us dua key jaisi is par aai hui musibat door kar deta hai, jab tak usney kisi gunah ya qata'-rehmi (rishta-naataa todney) ki dua na ki ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur Ubada bin Samit sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3382,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey achchha lagey (aur pasand aaye) ke masaayib aur mushkilat (aur takleef deh halaat) mein Allah uski duayen qubul kerey. to usey kushadgi aur faraakhi ki haalat mein kasrat sey duayen maangtey rehna chahiye.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
3383,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''sab sey behtar zikr (لا إلہ إلا اللہ) hai, aur behtareen dua (الحمد للہ) hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Musa bin Ibrahim ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Ali bin Madini aur kaee ney ye hadees Musa bin Ibrahim sey riwayat ki hai."
3384,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har waqt Allah ko yad kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Yahya bin Zakariya bin Abi zyada ki riwayat sey jantey hain.
3385,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi ko yad kar key uskey liye dua kartey, to pehley apney liye dua kartey phir uskey liye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3386,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam dua mein haath uthatey they to jab tak apney dono haath munh Mubarak par pher na letey unhen nichey na giraate they, Muhammad bin Musanna apni riwayat mein kehtey hain : aap dono haath jab dua key liye uthatey to unhen us waqt tak wapis na latey jab tak ke dono haath apney chehrey Mubarak par pher na letey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Hammad bin Esa ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Hammad bin Esa ney isey tanha riwayat kiya hai, aur ye bahut kam hadisein bayan kartey hain, un sey kaee logon ney riwayat li hai. 3- Hanzala ibne-Abi Sufiyan Jamhi Suqa (bharosemand) hain, unhen Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney Suqa (bharosemand) kaha hai."
3387,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey har kisi ki dua qubul ki jati hai, jab tak ke wo jaldi na machaey (jaldi ye hai ke) wo kehney lagta hai : mainey dua ki magar wo qubul na hui.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3388,"mainey Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aisa koi shakhs nahin hai jo har roz subah aur Sham ko (بسم الله الذي لا يضر مع اسمه شيء في الأرض wala في السماء وهو السميع العليم) ''main us Allah key naam key zariye sey panah maangta hun jis key naam ki barkat sey zamin aur aasman ki koi chiz nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakti, aur wo sunney wala jaan'ney wala hai.'' teen baar padhey aur usey koi chiz nuqsan pahuncha dey. Aban ko eik janib faaliz ka asar tha, (hadees sun kar) hadees sun'ney wala shakhs un ki taraf dekhney laga, Aban ney un sey kaha : miyan kya dekh rahey ho? hadees bilkul wesi hi hai jaisi mainey tum sey bayan ki hai. lekin baat ye hai ke jis din mujh par faaliz ka asar huwa us din mainey ye dua nahin padhi thi, aur nateeja ye huwa ke Allah ney mujh par apni taqdir ka faisla jari kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3389,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Sham key waqt kaha kerey (رضيت بالله ربا وبالإسلام دينا وبمحمد نبيا) ''main Allah key Rab honey, Islam key Deen honey aur Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Nabi honey par razi (aur khush) hun.''  to Allah par ye haq banta hai ke wo us bandey ko bhi apni taraf sey razi aur khush kar dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3390,"jab Sham hoti to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kehtey :(أمسينا وأمسى الملك لله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له أراه قال فيها له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير أسألك خير ما في هذه الليلة وخير ما بعدها وأعوذ بك من شر هذه الليلة وشر ما بعدها وأعوذ بك من الكسل وسوء الكبر وأعوذ بك من عذاب النار وعذاب القبر) ''hum ney Sham ki aur sari badshahi ney Sham ki Allah key hukm sey, tamam taareefen Allah key liye hain, Allah eik hai uskey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, usi key liye badshahat hai usi key liye hamd hai aur wo har chiz par qadir hai, us raat mein jo khair hai, uska main Talib hun, aur raat key baad ki bhi jo bhalai hai uska bhi main chahnewala hun, aur us raat ki burai aur raat key baad ki bhi burai sey main panah maangta hun, aur panah maangta hun main susti aur kaahili sey, aur panah maangta hun boodhaapey ki takleef sey, aur panah maangta hun aag key azab sey aur panah maangta hun qabr key azab sey.''  aur jab subah hoti to us waqt bhi yehi dua padhtey, thodi si tabdili key saath « أمسينا » ki jagah « أصبحنا » aur « أمسى » ki jagah « أصبح » kehtey « وأصبح الملك لله والحمد لله » ''subah ki hum ney, aur subh ki saari badshahi ney, aur sari tareefen Allah key liye hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, Shoba ney ye hadees isi sanad sey ibne-Masood sey riwayat ki hai, aur isey marfooan riwayat nahin kiya hai."
3391,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney Sahaba ko sikhatey huye kehtey they ke jab tumhari subah ho to kaho :« اللهم بك أصبحنا وبك أمسينا وبك نحيا وبك نموت وإليك المصير » ''aey Allah ! terey hukm sey hamney subah ki aur terey hi hukm sey hamney Sham ki, terey hukm sey hum zinda hain aur terey hi hukm sey hum mareingey.''  aur aap ney apney Sahaba ko sikhaya jab tum mein sey kisi ki Sham ho to usey chahiye ke kahey: « اللهم بك أمسينا وبك أصبحنا وبك نحيا وبك نموت وإليك النشور » ''hum ney terey hi hukm sey Sham ki aur terey hi hukm sey subah ki thi, terey hi hukm sey hum zinda hain aur tera jab hukm hoga, hum mar jaeyngey aur teri hi taraf hamein uth kar jana hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3392,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi aisi chiz bata dijiye jisey main subah aur Sham mein padh liya karun, aap ney farmaya : ''keh liya karo : (اللهم عالم الغيب والشهادة فاطر السموات والأرض رب كل شيء ومليكه أشهد أن لا إله إلا أنت أعوذ بك من شر نفسي ومن شر الشيطان وشركه) ''aey Allah ! ghaaieb aur hazir, mojud aur ghair mojud key jaan'ney waley , aasmano aur zamin key paida karney waley , har chiz key Malik ! main gawahi deta hun ke terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, main apney nafs key shar sey teri panah chahta hun, main shetan key shar aur uski dawate shirk sey teri panah chahta hun.''  aap ney farmaya : ''ye dua subah aur Sham aur jab apni khuwab gaah mein soney chalo padh liya karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3393,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''kya main tumhen (سيد الاستغفار) (talabe maghfirat ki duaaon mein sab sey aham dua) na bataaun? (wo ye hai) : (اللهم أنت ربي لا إله إلا أنت خلقتني وأنا عبدك وأنا على عهدك ووعدك ما استطعت أعوذ بك من شر ما صنعت وأبوء لك بنعمتك علي وأعترف بذنوبي فاغفر لي ذنوبي إنه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت) ''aey Allah ! to mera Rab hai, terey siwa mera koi mabood bar-haq nahin, tu ney mujhey paida kiya, main tera banda hun, main apni istataat bhar tujh sey kiye huye wade aur iqrar par qaaim hun, aur main teri zaat key zariye apney kiye key shar sey panah maangta hun tu ney mujhey jo nematen di hain, unka iqrar aur aetraaf karta hun, main apney gunahon ko taslim karta hun to merey gunahon ko maaf kar dey, kyonkey gunah to bas tu hi maaf kar sakta hai.''  Shaddad kehtey hain : aap ney farmaya : ''ye dua tum mein sey koi bhi Sham ko padhta hai aur subah honey sey pehley hi is par « qadr » ( maut ( aa jati hai to jannat uskey liye wajib ho jati hai, aur koi bhi shakhs aisa nahin hai jo is dua ko subah key waqt padhey aur Sham honey sey pehley usey « qadr » ( maut ( aa jaey magar ye ke jannat is par wajib ho jati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanadon sey Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar , ibne-Masood , ibne Abzi aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3394,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey kaha : kya main tumhen aisey kuchh kalimaat na sikhaun jinhen tum apney bistar par soney key liye janey lago to keh liya karo, agar tum usi raat mein mar jaao to fitrat par (yani Islam par) maro gey aur agar tum ney subah ki to subah ki, khair (ajr aur sawab) hasil kar key, tum kaho : (اللهم إني أسلمت نفسي إليك ووجهت وجهي إليك وفوضت أمري إليك رغبة ورهبة إليك وألجأت ظهري إليك لا ملجأ wala منجى منك إلا إليك آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت ونبيك الذي أرسلت) ''aey Allah ! mainey apni jaan terey hawaley kar di, main apna rukh teri taraf kar key puri tarah mutawajjeh ho gaya, mainey apna maamla teri supardagi mein dey diya, tujh sey umeeden wabasta kar key aur tera khof dil mein basa kar , meri peeth terey hawaley , terey siwa na merey liye koi jaey panah hai aur na hi tujh sey bach kar terey siwa koi thikana, main teri is kitab par eman laya jo tu ney utaari hai, main terey us Rasool par eman laya jisey tu ney Rasool bana kar bheja hai.'' Bara kehtey hain : mainey « نبيك الذي أرسلت » ki jagah « برسولك الذي أرسلت » keh diya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey seeney par apney haath sey کونچا , phir farmaya : « ونبيك الذي أرسلت ». Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai. 3- is hadees ko Mansoor bin Moa'tamir ney Saad bin Ubeda sey aur Saad ney Bara key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, albatta un ki riwayat mein itna farq hai ke jab tum apney bistar par aaoo aur tum wuzu sey ho to ye dua padha karo. 4- is bab mein Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
3395,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi apni daahini karwat letey phir padhey : (اللهم أسلمت نفسي إليك ووجهت وجهي إليك وألجأت ظهري إليك وفوضت أمري إليك لا ملجأ wala منجى منك إلا إليك أومن بكتابك وبرسولك) ''aey Allah ! mainey apni jaan terey supurd kar di, mainey apna munh ( auron ki taraf sey pher kar) teri taraf kar diya, mainey apni peeth teri taraf tek di, mainey apna maamla terey hawaley kar diya, tujh sey bach kar terey siwa aur koi jaey panah aur jaey najat nahin hai, main teri kitab aur terey Rasulon par eman lata hun.''  phir usi raat mein mar jaey, to wo jannat mein jaeyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3396,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab apney bistar par soney key liye aatey to kehtey : (الحمد لله الذي أطعمنا وسقانا وكفانا وآوانا فكم ممن لا كافي له wala مؤوي) ''tamam taareefen us Allah key liye hain jisney hum ko khilaya aur pilaya aur bachaya hum ko) makhluq key shar sey (aur hum ko) rehney sehney key liye ( thikana diya, jabke kitney hi aisey log hain jinka na koi himayati aur muhafiz hai aur na hi koi thikana aur jaey rihaaish.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3397,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney bistar par soney key liye jaatey huye teen baar kahey : (أستغفر الله العظيم الذي لا إله إلا هو الحي القيوم وأتوب إلي) ''main us azeem tareen Allah sey istighfar karta hun ke jis key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, wo hamesha zinda aur hamesha qaaim aur hamesha rehney wala hai, aur main usi ki taraf ruju hota hun.''  Allah uskey gunah bakhsh dega agar-che wo gunah samandar ki jhaag ki tarah (beshumaar) hon, agar-che wo gunah darkht key patton ki tadaad mein hon, agar-che wo gunah ikhatta ret key zarron ki tadaad mein hon, agar-che wo duniya key dino key barabar hon. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf is sanad sey Ubedullah bin Waleed ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3398,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab soney ka irada kartey to apna haath apney sar key nichey rakhtey, phir padhtey : « اللهم قني عذابك يوم تجمع أو تبعث عبادك » ''aey Allah ! mujhey to us din key azab sey bacha ley jis din to apney bandon ko jama kerega ya uthaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3399,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sotey waqt apney dahiney haath ka takiya banatey they, phir padhtey they : (رب قني عذابك يوم تبعث عبادك) ''aey merey Rab ! mujhey us din key azab sey bacha ley jis din ke to mardon ko utha kar zinda kerega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees (Imam) Sory ney Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat ki, aur Abu-Is'haq ney Bara sey  aur Imam Sory ney un dono yani Abu-Is'haq aur Bara key beech mein kisi aur Raavi ka zikr nahin kiya. 3- riwayat ki Shoba ney Abu-Is'haq sey , aur Abu-Is'haq ney abu-Ubaida sey , aur eik doosrey shakhs ney Bara sey. 4- Israel ney Abu-Is'haq sey , aur Abu-Is'haq ney Abdullah bin Yazeed key wastey sey Bara sey riwayat ki hai, aur Abu-Is'haq ney abu-Ubaida aur abu-Ubaida ney Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi ki tarah riwayat ki."
3400,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamein hukm detey they ke jab hum mein sey koi apney bistar par soney key liye jaey to kahey : (اللهم رب السموات ورب الأرضين وربنا ورب كل شيء وفالق الحب والنوى ومنزل التوراة والإنجيل والقرآن أعوذ بك من شر كل ذي شر أنت آخذ بناصيته أنت الأول فليس قبلك شيء وأنت الآخر فليس بعدك شيء والظاهر فليس فوقك شيء والباطن فليس دونك شيء اقض عني الدين وأغنني من الفقر) ''aey aasmano aur zaminon key Rab ! aey hamarey Rab ! aey har chiz key Rab ! zamin cheer kar daaney aur guthli sey paudey uganey waley,Tauraat, Injeel aur Quran nazil karney waley , aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun har shar wali chiz key shar sey, tu hi har shar aur fasad ki peshani apni giraft mein ley sakta hai. tu hi sab sey pehley hai tujh sey pehley koi chiz nahin hai, tu hi sab sey aakhir hai, terey baad koi chiz nahin hai, to sab sey zahir (oopper) hai terey ooper koi chiz nahin hai, to baatin (neechey aur poshida) hai terey sey nichey koi chiz nahin hai, mujh par jo qarz hai usey to ada kar dey aur to mujhey mohtaj sey nikal kar ghani kar dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3401,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab koi tum mein sey apney bistar par sey uth jaey phir lot kar is par (letney, bethney) aaye to usey chahiye ke apney izaar (tehband, lungi) key (pallu) koney aur kinarey sey teen baar bistar ko jhaad dey, isliye ke usey kuchh pata nahin ke uskey uth kar janey key baad wahan kon si chiz aa kar bethi ya chupi hai, phir jab letey to kahey : (باسمك ربي وضعت جنبي وبك أرفعه فإن أمسكت نفسي فارحمها وإن أرسلتها فاحفظها بما تحفظ به عبادك الصالحين) ''aey merey Rab ! main tera naam ley kar (apney bistar par) apney pehlu ko dal raha hun yani soney ja raha hun, aur tera hi naam ley kar main isey uthaaunga bhi, phir agar to meri jaan ko (soney hi ki haalat mein) rok leta hai (yani mujhey maut dey deta hai) to meri jaan par reham farma, aur agar to soney deta hai to uski wesi hi hifazat farma jaisi ke to apney nek aur Saleh bandon ki hifazat karta hai.''  phir neend sey bedaar ho jaey to usey chahiye ke kahey : (الحمد لله الذي عافاني في جسدي ورد علي روحي وأذن لي بذكره) ''tamam tareefen us Allah key liye hain jisney merey badan ko sehat mand rakha , aur meri rooh mujh par lota di aur mujhey apni yad ki ijazat (aur tofiq) di.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees hadees Hasan hai. 2- baaz doosrey raawiyon ney bhi ye hadees riwayat ki hai, aur is riwayat mein unhoney « فلينفضه بداخلة إزاره » ka lafz istimal kiya hai « بداخلة إزاره » sey murad tehband ka andar wala hissa hai. 3- is bab mein Jaafar aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3402,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har raat jab apney bistar par aatey to apni dono hatheliyan ikhatti kartey , phir un dono par ye suraten : « قل هو الله أحد » , padhi. « قل أعوذ برب الفلق » aur « قل أعوذ برب الناس  padh kar phunk maartay , phir un dono hatheliyon ko apney jism par jahan tak wo pahunchti phertey, aur shuru kartey apney sar , chehrey aur badan key agley hissey sey , aur aisa aap teen baar kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3403,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar unhoney kaha : aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi aisi chiz bataiye jisey main jab apney bistar par janey lagun to padh liya karun, aap ney farmaya : « قل يا أيها الكافرون » padh liya karo, kyonkey is Sura mein shirk sey najat hai. Shoba kehtey hain : (hamarey ustad) Abu-Is'haq kabhi kehtey hain ke Sura « قل يا أيها الكافرون » eik baar padh liya karo, aur kabhi eik baar ka zikr nahin kartey."
3404,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam us waqt tak sotey na they jab tak ke soney sey pehley aap Sura (sajda) aur Sura (تبارک الذی) ( yani Sura Mulk) padh na letey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sufiyan (Sory) aur kuchh doosrey logon ney bhi ye hadees Les sey , Les ney abu-Zubair sey , abu-Zubair ney Jabir key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 2- Zuhair ney bhi ye hadees abu-Zubair sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehtey hain ke mainey un sey kaha : kya aap ney ye hadees Jabir sey (khud) suni hai? to unhoney kaha ke mainey ye hadees Jabir sey nahin suni hai, mainey ye hadees Safwan ya ibne Safwan sey suni hai. 3- shaaba ney Mughira bin Muslim sey, Mughira ney abu-Zubair sey aur abu-Zubair ney Jabir sey Les ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai."
3405,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Sura Zumar aur Sura Bani-Israel jab tak padh na letey sotey na they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mujhey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney khabar di hai ke abu-Lubaba ka naam Marwan hai, aur ye Abdur-Rehman bin Ziyad key azad karda ghulam hain, unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey suna hai aur un (Abu-Lubaba) sey Hammad bin Zaid ney suna hai."
3406,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab tak (Musabbihaat) padh na letey sotey na they, aap farmatey they : ''in main eik aisi aayat hai jo hazar aayaton sey behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3407,"main Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) key sath eik safar mein tha, unhoney kaha : kya main tumhen aisi chiz na sikhaaun jisey hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sikhatey they, aap ney hamein sikhaya ke hum kahin : (اللهم إني أسألك الثبات في الأمر وأسألك عزيمة الرشد وأسألك شكر نعمتك وحسن عبادتك وأسألك لسانا صادقا وقلبا سليما وأعوذ بك من شر ما تعلم وأسألك من خير ما تعلم وأستغفرك مما تعلم إنك أنت علام الغيوب) ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey kaam mein mazbooti (thehrao)  ki tofiq maangta hun, main tujh sey neki aur bhalai ki pukhtagi chahta hun, main chahta hun ke to mujhey apni nemat key shukriya ki tofiq dey, apni achchhi ibadat karney ki tofiq dey, main tujh sey saadiq aur qalbe Saleem ka Talib hun, main teri panah chahta hun us shar sey jo terey ilm mein hai aur us khair ka bhi main tujh sey talabgar hun jo terey ilm mein hai aur tujh sey maghfirat maangta hun un gunahon ki jinhen to janta hai to beshak sari poshida baaton ka jaan'ney wala hai."
3408,"Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) ney mujh sey aataa peesney key sabab haathon mein aabley (chhaaley) pad jaaney ki shikayat ki, mainey un sey kaha : kaash! aap apney Abu-jaan key paas jatin aur aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey apney liye eik khaadim mang letin, (wo gaeen to) aap ney (jawab mein) farmaya : ''kya main tum dono ko aisi chiz na bata dun jo tum dono key liye khaadim sey ziyada behtar aur aaram deh ho, jab tum dono apney bistaron par soney key liye jaao to 33 baar Alhamdulillah aur Subhan-Allah aur 34 baar Allahu-Akbar keh liya karo, is hadees main eik taweel qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibn Aun ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees kaee aur sanadon sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai."
3409,(aap ki beti) Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas apney haathon mein aabley (chhaale) pad janey ki shikayat karney aayin to aap ney unhen tasbih (Subhan Allah) takbir (Allahu-Akbar) aur tahmeed (Alhamdulillah) padhney ka hukm diya.
3410,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''do aadatein aisi hain jinhen jo bhi musalman pabandi aur pukhtagi sey apnaaey rahega wo jannat mein jaeyga, dhiyan sey sun lo, dono aasan hain magar un par amal karney waley thodey hain, har namaz key baad das baar Allah ki tasbih karey (Subhan Allah kahey) das baar hamd bayan karey (Alhamdulillah kahey) aur das baar Allah ki badai bayan karey (Allahu-Akbar kahey). Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko unhen apni ungliyon par shumar kartey huye dekha hai, aap ney farmaya : ''ye to zaban sey gin'ney mein dedh sau huye lekin ye (das guna badh kar) meezaan mein dedh hazar ho jaeyngey. (ye eik khaslat aur aadat hui) aur (doosri khaslat aur aadat ye hai ke) jab tum bistar par soney jaao to sau baar Subhan Allah, Allahu-Akbar aur Alhamdulillah kaho, ye zaban sey kehney main to sau hain lekin meezaan mein hazar hain, (ab bataao) kon hai tum mein jo din aur raat dhaai-hazaar hazar gunah karta ho? logon ney kaha : hum isey hamesha aur pabandi key sath kyon nahin kar sakengey? aap ney farmaya : ''(is wajeh sey) ke tum mein sey koi namaz padh raha hota hai, shetan uskey paas aata hai aur us sey kehta hai : falan baat ko yad karo, falan chiz ko soch lo, yahan tak ke wo uski tawajjoh asal kaam sey hata deta hai, taake wo usey na kar sakey, aisey hi aadmi apney bistar par hota hai aur shetan aa kar usey (thapkiyan dey-dey kar) sulaata rehta hai yahan tak ke wo (baghair tasbeehaat padhey) so jata hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba aur Sory ney ye hadees Ata bin Saaib sey riwayat ki hai. aur Aamash ney ye hadees Ata bin Saaib sey ikhtisaar key sath riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Zaid bin Sabit , Anas aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3411,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko tasbih (Subhan Allah) ungliyon par gintey huye dekha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Aamash ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai.
3412,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kuchh cheezen namaz key peechhey (baad mein) padhney ki aisi hain ke unka kehney wala mehroom aur na-murad nahin rehta, har namaz key baad 33 baar Subhan Allah kahey, 33 baar Alhamdulillah kahey, aur 34 baar Allahu-Akbar kahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Shoba ney ye hadees Hukm sey riwayat ki hai, aur usey marfoo nahin kiya hai, aur Mansoor bin Moa'tamir ney Hukm sey riwayat ki hai aur isey marfoo kiya hai."
3413,"hamen hukm diya gaya ke har namaz key baad hum (salam pher kar) 33 baar Subhan-Allah, 33 baar Alhamdulillah aur 34 baar Allahu-Akbar kahin , Raavi ( Zaid ( kehtey hain ke eik Ansari ney khuwab dekha , khuwab mein nazar aaney waley shakhs (farishte) ney puchha : kya tumhen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya hai ke har namaz key baad 33 baar Subhan-Allah 33 baar Alhamdulillah aur 34 baar Allahu-Akbar keh liya karo? usney kaha : haan, (to saail (farishtey) ney kaha : (33, 33 aur 34 key bajaey) 25 kar lo , aur (لا إلہ إلا اللہ) ko bhi inhin key sath shamil kar lo, (is tarah kul sau ho jaeyngey) subah jab hui to wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaey, aur aap sey ye waqia bayan kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''aisa hi kar lo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3414,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab koi neend sey jaagey phir kahey :(لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير وسبحان الله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر wala حول wala قوة إلا بالله)  phir kahey (رب اغفر لي) ''aey merey Rab hamein bakhsh dey'' , ya aap ney kaha : phir wo dua karey to uski dua qubul ki jaeygi, phir agar usney himmat ki aur wuzu kiya phir namaz padhi to uski namaz maqbool hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3415,"Umair bin Haani har din hazar rakatein namazein padhtey they, aur sau hazar (yani eik lakh) tasbeehaat padhtey they, yani Subhan Allah kehtey they."
3416,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key darwazey key paas sota tha, aur aap ko wuzu ka pani diya karta tha, main aap ko « Samiallahu-liman-hamida » kehtey huye sunta tha, neez main aap ko « Al-hamdulillahi-Rabbil-Aalamin » padhtey huye sunta tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3417,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab soney ka irada farmatey to kehtey : (اللهم باسمك أموت وأحيا)aur jab aap so kar uthtey to kehtey : (الحمد لله الذي أحيا نفسي بعد ما أماتها وإليه النشور). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3418,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab raat mein tahajjud key liye uthtey to ye dua padhtey : اللهم لك الحمد أنت نور السموات والأرض ولك الحمد أنت قيام السموات والأرض ولك الحمد أنت رب السموات والأرض ومن فيهن أنت الحق ووعدك الحق ولقاؤك حق والجنة حق والنار حق والساعة حق اللهم لك أسلمت وبك آمنت وعليك توكلت وإليك أنبت وبك خاصمت وإليك حاكمت فاغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت وما أسررت وما أعلنت أنت إلهي لا إله إلا أنت'' aey Allah ! terey hi liye sab tareef hai tu hi aasmano aur zamin ka Noor hai, (aur aasman o zamin key darmiyan roshni paida karney wala ( terey hi liye sab tareef hai tu hi aasmano aur zamin ko qaaim karney wala hai, terey liye hi sab tareef hai to aasmano aur zamin ka aur jo kuch un dono key darmiyan hai sabka rab hai, to haq hai tera wada haq ( sacha ( hai teri mulaqat haq hai, jannat haq hai jahannam haq hai, qiyamat haq hai. aey Allah ! mainey apney ko terey supurd kar diya, aur tujh hi par eman laya , aur tujh hi par bharosa kya, aur teri hi taraf ruju kya, aur terey hi khatir mein ladaa aur terey hi paas faisla key liye gaya . aey Allah ! main pehley jo kuch kar chuka hun aur jo kuch baad mein karunga aur jo poshida karun aur jo khuley aam karun merey sarey gunah aur khataeyn maaf kar dey, tu hi mera mabood hai, aur terey siwa mera koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey aai hai, aur wo usey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
3419,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko eik raat namaz ( tahajjud ( sey farigh ho kar padhtey huye suna (aap padh rahey they ( : اللهم إني أسألك رحمة من عندك تهدي بها قلبي وتجمع بها أمري وتلم بها شعثي وتصلح بها غائبي وترفع بها شاهدي وتزكي بها عملي وتلهمني بها رشدي وترد بها ألفتي وتعصمني بها من كل سوء اللهم أعطني إيمانا ويقينا ليس بعده كفر ورحمة أنال بها شرف كرامتك في الدنيا والآخرة اللهم إني أسألك الفوز في العطاء ونزل الشهداء وعيش السعداء والنصر على الأعداء اللهم إني أنزل بك حاجتي وإن قصر رأيي وضعف عملي افتقرت إلى رحمتك فأسألك يا قاضي الأمور ويا شافي الصدور كما تجير بين البحور أن تجيرني من عذاب السعير ومن دعوة الثبور ومن فتنة القبور اللهم ما قصر عنه رأيي ولم تبلغه نيتي ولم تبلغه مسألتي من خير وعدته أحدا من خلقك أو خير أنت معطيه أحدا من عبادك فإني أرغب إليك فيه وأسألكه برحمتك رب العالمين اللهم ذا الحبل الشديد والأمر الرشيد أسألك الأمن يوم الوعيد والجنة يوم الخلود مع المقربين الشهود الركع السجو د الموفين بالعهود إنك رحيم ودود وأنت تفعل ما تريد اللهم اجعلنا هادين مهتدين غير ضالين wala مضلين سلما لأوليائك وعدوا لأعدائك نحب بحبك من أحبك ونعادي بعداوتك من خالفك اللهم هذا الدعا وعليك الإجابة وهذا الجهد وعليك التكلان اللهم اجعل لي نورا في قلبي ونورا في قبري ونورا من بين يدي ونورا من خلفي ونورا an يميني ونورا an شمالي ونورا من فوقي ونورا من تحتي ونورا في سمعي ونورا في بصري ونورا في شعري ونورا في بشري ونورا في لحمي ونورا في دمي ونورا في عظامي اللهم أعظم لي نورا وأعطني نورا واجعل لي نورا سبحان الذي تعطف العز وقال به سبحان الذي لبس المجد وتكرم به سبحان الذي لا ينبغي التسبيح إلا له سبحان ذي al-Fazal والنعم سبحان ذي المجد والكرم سبحان ذي الجلال والإكرامImam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai aur hum isey ibne-Abi Leila ki riwayat sey isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Shoba aur Sufiyan Sory ney Salma bin kuheil sey, Salma ney Kureb sey, aur Kureb ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is hadees key baaz hisson ki riwayat ki hai, unhoney ye puri lambi hadees zikr nahin ki hai. faeyda padhi. : ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey aisi rehmat ka Talib hun, jis key zariey to merey dil ko hidayat ata kar dey , aur jis key zariey merey mamley ko mujtama o mustehkam kar dey, merey paraganda maamlon ko durust farma dey, aur uskey zariey merey baatin ki islah farma dey , aur uskey zariey merey zahir ko buland kar dey , aur uskey zariey merey amal ko saaf suthra bana dey , uskey zariey sidhi raah ki taraf meri rehnumai farma , uskey zariey hamari bahami (aapsi) ulfat o chaahat ko lota dey , aur uskey zariey har burai sey mujhey bacha ley , aey Allah ! to hamen aisa eman o yaqin dey ke phir uskey baad kufr ki taraf jana na ho, aey Allah ! to hamen aisi rehmat ata kar jiskey zariey main duniya o aakhirat mein teri karaamat ka sharf hasil kar sakun, aey Allah ! main tujh sey « Ata » ( bakhshish (aur « qaza » ( faisley ( mein kamiyabi maangta hun, main tujh sey shohda ki si mehman nawaazi, nek bakhton ki si khushgawar zindagi aur dushmanon key khilaf teri madad ka khwastgar hun, aur main agar-che kam samajh aur kamzor amal ka aadmi hun magar main apni zaruriyat ko leykar terey hi paas pahunchta hun, main teri rehmat ka mohtaj hun, aey maamlat key niptaney o faisla karney waley ! aey seenon ki bimariyon sey shifaa deney waley to mujhey bacha ley jahannam ki aag sey, tabahi o barbadi ki pukar (nauha o maatam) sey, aur qabron key fitnon azab aur munkar nakeer key sawalat sey isi tarah bacha ley jis tarah ke to samandaron mein (ghirey aur tufanon key andar phansey huye logon ko) bachata hai, aey Allah! jis chiz tak pahunchney sey meri raey aql qasir rahi, jis chiz tak meri niyat o iradey ki bhi rasai na ho saki, jis bhalai ka tu ney apni makhluq mein sey kisi sey wada kya aur main usey tujh sey mang na saka, ya jo bhalai to az khud apney bandon mein sey kisi bandey ko deney wala hai main bhi usey tujh sey maangney aur paney ki khahish aur aarzu karta hun, aur aey rabbul-aalmin! sarey jahan key paalanhaar, teri rehmat key saharey tujh sey us chiz ka sawali hun, aey Allah badi quwat waley aur achey kamon waley , main tujh sey waeed key din yani qiyamat key din aman o chain chahta hun, main tujh sey hamesha key liye terey muqarrab bandon, terey kalma bhale hi bandon, terey aagey jhukney waley bandon , terey samney sajda rez honey waley bandon , terey wada o iqrar key paband bandon key sath jannat mein janey ki dua maangta hun, (aey rab ! ( to Rahim hai) bandon par reham karney wala ( to Wadud hai) apney bandon sey mohabbat farmanewala ( to (ba-khtiyar hai) jo chahta hai karta hai, aey Allah! to hamen hidayat deney wala bana magar aisa jo khud bhi hidayat yafta ho jo na khud gumrah ho, na dusron ko gumrah bananey wala ho, terey doston key liye suleh jo ho, aur terey dushmanon key liye dushman, jo shakhs tujh sey mohabbat rakhta ho hum us shakhs sey tujh sey mohabbat rakhney key sabab mohabbat rakhen , aur jo shakhs terey khilaf karey hum us shakhs sey tujh sey dushmani rakhney key sabab dushmani rakhen , aey Allah ye hamari dua o darkhaast hai, aur us dua ko qubul karna bas terey hi haath mein hai, ye hamari koshish hai aur bharosa bas teri hi zaat par hai, aey Allah ! to meri qabr mein Noor ( roshni ( kar dey , aey Allah ! to merey qalb mein Noor bhar dey , aey Allah ! to merey aagey aur samney Noor phela dey , aey Allah to merey peechey Noor kar dey , merey aagey aur samney Noor phela dey , aey Allah to merey peechey Noor kar dey , Noor merey dahiney bhi Noor merey baain bhi, Noor merey ooper bhi aur Noor merey nichey bhi, Noor merey kanon mein bhi Noor meri aakhon mein bhi, Noor merey baalon mein bhi Noor merey khaal mein bhi Noor , merey gosht mein bhi, Noor merey khoon mein bhi aur Noor mein izafa farma dey , merey liye Noor bana dey , pak hai wo zaat jisney izzat ko apna odhna banaya , aur izzat hi ko apna shiaar bananey ka hukm diya, pak hai wo zaat jisney buzurgi o sharf ko apna libas banaya aur jis key sabab sey wo mukarram o sharf wala huwa , pak hai wo zaat jis key siwa kisi aur key liye tasbih sazawar nahin, pak hai Fazal aur nematon wala , pak hai buzurgi o karam wala , pak hai azmat o buzurgi wala ''."
3420,"mainey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : raat mein jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tahajjud padhney key liye khadey hotey they to apni namaz key shuru mein kya padhtey they? unhoney kaha : jab raat ko khadey hotey , namaz shuru kartey waqt ye dua padhtey :اللهم رب جبريل وميكائيل وإسرافيل فاطر السموات والأرض عالم الغيب والشهادة أنت تحكم بين عبادك فيما كانوا فيه يختلفون اهدني لما اختلف فيه من الحق بإذنك إنك تهدي من تشاء إلى صراط مستقيم''aey Allah ! Jibreel , mekael o Israafeel key rab ! aasmano aur zamin key paida karney waley, chupey aur khuley key janney waley , apney bandon key darmiyan unkey ikhtilafat ka faisla karney wala hai, aey Allah! jis chiz mein bhi ikhtilaf huwa hai is mein haq ko apnaney , haq ko qubul karney ki apney izn o hukm sey mujhey hidayat farma, (tofiq dey) kyonkey tu hi jisey chahta hai sidhi raah par chalata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3421,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz mein khadey hotey to padhtey : (وجهت وجهي للذي فطر السموات والأرض حنيفا وما أنا من المشركين إن صلاتي ونسكي ومحياي ومماتي لله رب العالمين لا شريك له وبذلك أمرت وأنا من المسلمين اللهم أنت الملك لا إله إلا أنت أنت ربي وأنا عبدك zulmat نفسي واعترفت بذنبي فاغفر لي ذنوبي جميعا إنه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت واهدني لأحسن الأخلاق لا يهدي لأحسنها إلا أنت واصرف عني سيئها إنه لا يصرف عني سيئها إلا أنت آمنت بك تباركت وتعاليت أستغفرك وأتوب إليك)phir jab aap rukoo kartey to padhtey : « اللهم لك ركعت وبك آمنت ولك أسلمت خشع لك سمعي وبصري ومخي وعظامي وعصبي » phir aap jab sar uthatey to kehtey : (اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ملء السموات والأرضين وملء ما بينهما وملء ما شئت من شيء بعد), ‏phir jab aap sajda farmatey to kehtey : « اللهم لك سجدت وبك آمنت ولك أسلمت سجد وجهي للذي خلقه فصوره وشق سمعه وبصره فتبارك الله أحسن الخالقين » phir aap sab sey aakhir mein tashahud aur salam key darmiyan jo dua padhtey they, wo dua ye thi : « اللهم اغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت وما أسررت وما أعلنت وما أنت أعلم به مني أنت المقدم وأنت المؤخر la إله إلا أنت » . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3422,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to ( takbir tahreema key baad) kehtey : ( وجهت وجهي للذي فطر السموات والأرض حنيفا وما أنا من المشركين إن صلاتي ونسكي ومحياي ومماتي لله رب العالمين لا شريك له وبذلك أمرت وأنا من المسلمين اللهم أنت الملك لا إله إلا أنت أنت ربي وأنا عبدك zulmat نفسي واعترفت بذنبي فاغفر لي ذنوبي جميعا إنه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت واهدني لأحسن الأخلاق لا يهدي لأحسنها إلا أنت واصرف عني سيئها لا يصرف عني سيئها إلا أنت لبيك وسعديك والخير كله في يديك والشر ليس إليك أنا بك وإليك تباركت وتعاليت أستغفرك وأتوب إليك )phir jab aap rukoo kartey to padhtey : (اللهم لك ركعت وبك آمنت ولك أسلمت خشع لك سمعي وبصري وعظامي وعصبي)phir jab aap rukoo sey sar uthatey to aap kehtey : (اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ملء السماء وملء الأرض وملء ما بينهما وملء ما شئت من شيء), phir jab sajda mein jatey to kehtey : (اللهم لك سجدت وبك آمنت ولك أسلمت سجد وجهي للذي خلقه فصوره وشق سمعه وبصره فتبارك الله أحسن الخالقين)phir aap sab sey aakhir mein tashahud aur salam key darmiyan padhtey : (اللهم اغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت وما أسررت وما أعلنت وما أسرفت وما أنت أعلم به مني أنت المقدم وأنت المؤخر لا إله إلا أنت). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3423,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab farz namaz padhney khadey hotey they to apney dono haath apney dono kandhon key barabar uthatey ( rafaa-yadein kartey ( , aur aisa us waqt bhi kartey they jab apni qirat puri kar letey they aur rukoo ka irada kartey they, aur aisa hi kartey they jab rukoo sey sar uthatey they padhi. , bethey honey ki haalat main apni namaz key kisi hissey mein bhi rafaa-yadein na kartey they, phir jab dono sajdey karkey khadey hotey to apney dono haath uthatey usi tarah, phir takbir (Allahu-akbar) kehtey aur namaz shuru kartey waqt takbir (tahreema) key baad padhtey : (وجهت وجهي للذي فطر السموات والأرض حنيفا وما أنا من المشركين إن صلاتي ونسكي ومحياي ومماتي لله رب العالمين لا شريك له وبذلك أمرت وأنا من المسلمين اللهم أنت الملك لا إله إلا أنت سبحانك أنت ربي وأنا عبدك zulmat نفسي واعترفت بذنبي فاغفر لي ذنوبي جميعا إنه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت واهدني لأحسن الأخلاق لا يهدي لأحسنها إلا أنت واصرف عني سيئها لا يصرف عني سيئها إلا أنت لبيك وسعديك أنا بك وإليك wala منجا wala ملجأ إلا إليك أستغفرك وأتوب إليك)(ye dua padhney key baad) phir qirat kartey , rukoo mein jatey , rukoo mein aap ye dua padhtey : (اللهم لك ركعت وبك آمنت ولك أسلمت وأنت ربي خشع سمعي وبصري ومخي وعظمي لله رب العالمين) phir jab aap apna sar rukoo sey uthatey to kehtey : « samiallahu-liman hamida » , padhi. « samiallahu-liman hamida » kehney key fauran baad aap padhtey : (اللهم ربنا ولك الحمد ملء السموات والأرض وملء ما شئت من شيء) uskey baad jab sajda kartey to sajdon mein padhtey : « اللهم لك سجدت وبك آمنت ولك أسلمت وأنت ربي سجد وجهي للذي خلقه وشق سمعه وبصره تبارك الله أحسن الخالقين » aur jab namaz sey salam pherney chaltey to ( salam pherney sey pehley ( padhtey : « اللهم اغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت وما أسررت وما أعلنت أنت إلهي la إله إلا أنت » . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur usi par amal hai Imam Shafai aur hamarey baaz as-haab ka, 3- Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal aisa khayal nahin rakhtay, 4- ehle-koofa aur unkey ilawa key baaz ulama ka kehna hai ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unhen nafli namazon mein padhtey they na ke farz namazon mein 5- mainey abu-Ismaail Tirmizi Muhammad bin Ismail bin Yusuf ko kehtey huye suna hai ke mainey Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud haashmii ko kehtey huye suna , unhoney zikr kya usi hadees ka phir kaha : ye hadees merey nazdik aisey hi mustanad aur qawi hai, jaisey Zohri ki wo hadees qawi o mustanda hoti hai jisey wo Salim bin Abdullah sey aur Salim apney baap sey riwayat kartey hain."
3424,"eik shakhs ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! main soya huwa tha, raat mainey apney aap ko khuwab mein dekha to un main eik darkht key peechey namaz padh raha hun, mainey sajda kya to darkht ney bhi merey sajdey ki mutaabiat kartey huye sajda kya, mainey suna wo padh raha tha : (اللهم اكتب لي بها عندك أجرا وضع عني بها وزرا واجعلها لي عندك ذخرا وتقبلها مني كما تقبلتها من عبدك داود) ''aey Allah! to uskey badley merey liye apney paas ajr o sawab likh ley , aur uskey iwaz mujh par sey) gunahon ka ( bojh utaar dey aur usey apney paas ( merey liye aakhirat ka ( zakhira bana dey , aur usey merey liye aisey hi qubul kar ley jis tarah tu ney apney bandey Dawud (Alaihissalam) key liye qubul kya tha ''. ibne-Jurej kehtey hain : mujh sey tumharey ( yani Hasan bin Ubedullah key ( dada ( Ubedullah ( ney kaha ke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (us moqey par) sajdey ki eik aayat padhi , phir sajda kya, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : mainey aap ko) sajdey mein) padhtey huye suna aap wohi dua padh rahey they, jo ( khuwab waley ( aadmi ney aap ko darkht ki dua sunai thi padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey kisi aur sey nahin sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3425,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat key waqt sajda tilawat mein padhtey they : « سجد وجهي للذي خلقه وشق سمعه وبصره بحوله وقوته » '' mera chehra uskey aagey sajda rez huwa jisney usey apni qudrat o quwat sey paida kya, jisney usey sunney key liye kaan aur dekhney key liye aankhen din ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3426,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs ghar sey nikaltey waqt : (بسم الله توكلت على الله لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله) ''main ney Allah key naam sey shuru kya, mainey Allah par bharosa kya aur gunahon sey bachney aur kisi neki key baja laney ki qudrat o quwat nahin hai siwaye Allah key saharey key'' kahey , us sey kaha jaeyga : tumhari kifaayat kar di gaee , aur tum ( dushman key shar sey) bacha liye gaey, aur shetan tum sey door ho gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3427,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab ghar sey nikaltey to ye dua padhtey they : (بسم الله توكلت على الله اللهم إنا نعوذ بك من أن نزل أو نضل أو نظلم أو نظلم أو نجهل أو يجهل علينا)''shuru karta hun Allah key naam sey, bharosa karta hun Allah par, aey Allah teri panah chahta hun is baat sey ke haq o sawaab sey kahin phir na jaaun, ya raahe-haq sey bhatka na diya jaaun, ya main kisi par zulm karun ya mujh par zulm kya jaey, ya main kisi key sath jahilana bartaw karun ya koi merey sath jahilana andaz sey pesh aaye''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3428,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney baazar mein dakhil hotey waqt ye dua padhi : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو حي لا يموت بيده الخير وهو على كل شيء قدير) ''nahin koi mabood bar-haq hai magar Allah akela , uska koi shareek nahin hai, usi key liye mulk (badshahat) hai aur usi key liye hamd o sana hai wohi zinda karta aur wohi maarta hai, wo zinda hai kabhi marega nahin, usi key haath mein sari bhalaiyan hain, aur wo har chiz par qudrat rakhta hai'', to Allah Taala uskey liye das lakh nekiyan likhta hai aur uski das lakh buraiyan mita deta hai aur uskey das lakh darjey buland farmata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Amr bin Dinar Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar walon key aamad o kharch key muntazim they, unhoney ye hadees Salim bin Abdullah sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
3429,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs bazar jatey huye ye dua padhey : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو حي لا يموت بيده الخير وهو على كل شيء قدير) to Allah uskey liye das lakh nekiyan likh dega aur das lakh uskey gunah mita dega aur jannat mein uskey liye eik ghar banaeyga . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye Amr bin Dinar Basraa Shekh hain, aur baaz as-haab hadees ney unkey barey mein kalam kya hai 2- Yahya bin Sulem Taaifi ney ye hadees Imran bin Muslim sey , Imran ney Abdullah bin Dinar sey , aur Abdullah bin Dinar ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aur is mein unhoney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ka zikr nahin kya hai."
3430,"mein gawahi deta hun ke abu Saeed Khudri aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma ney gawahi di ke un dono ki mojudgi mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo « لا إله إلا الله والله أكبر » '' Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, Allah sab sey bada hai'' , kehta hai to uska rab uski tasdeeq karta hai aur kehta hai : ( haan ( merey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, main hi sab sey bada hun, aur jab : « لا إله إلا الله وحده » '' Allah wahid key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai'' , kehta hai, to aap ney farmaya : '' Allah kehta hai) haan ( mujh tanha key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, aur jab kehta hai : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له) '' Allah wahid key siwa koi mabood nahin hai uska koi shareek o saajhi nahin'' , to Allah kehta hai, ( haan ( mujhey tanha key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, aur mera koi shareek nahin hai, aur jab kehta hai : « لا إله إلا الله له الملك » '' Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, usi key liye badshahat hai aur usi key liye hamd hai'' , to Allah kehta hai : koi mabood bar-haq nahin magar main , merey liye hi badshahat hai aur merey liye hi hamd hai, aur jab kehta hai : (لا إله إلا الله wala حول wala قوة إلا بالله) ''Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, aur gunah sey bachney aur bhaley kaam karney ki taqat nahin hai, magar Allah Taala ki tofiq sey '', to Allah kehta hai : ( haan ( merey siwa koi mabood nahin hai aur gunahon sey bachney aur bhaley kaam karney ki quwat nahin hai magar meri tofiq sey, aur aap farmatey they : jo un kalmaat ko apni bimari mein kahey , aur mar jaey to aag usey na khayegi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3431,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs musibat mein giraftar kisi shakhs ko dekhey aur kahey : (الحمد لله الذي عافاني مما ابتلاك به وفضلني على كثير ممن خلق تفضيلا)'' sab tareef Allah key liye hai ke jisney mujhey us bula o musibat sey bachaya jis sey tujhey dochaar kya, aur mujhey fazilat di, apni bahut si makhluqat par '' , to wo zindagi bhar har bula o musibat sey mehfooz rahega chahey wo kaisi ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- aur Amr bin Dinar aal Zuber key khazaanchi hain aur Basra Shekh hain aur hadees mein ziyada qawi nahin hain, aur ye Salim bin Abdullah bin umr sey kaee ahadees ki riwayat mein munfarid hain, 3- abu Jaafar Muhammad bin Ali sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jab aadmi kisi ko musibat mein giraftar dekhey to us bula sey aahista sey panah maangey musibat zada shakhs ko na sunaiye , 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3432,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs kisi shakhs ko musibat mein mubtala dekhey phir kahey : (الحمد لله الذي عافاني مما ابتلاك به وفضلني على كثير ممن خلق تفضيلا) to usey ye bula na pahunchegi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai.
3433,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs kisi majlis mein bethey aur us sey bahut si laghw aur behuda baaten ho jaeyn, aur wo apni majlis sey uth janey sey pehley padh ley : (سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك أشهد أن لا إله إلا أنت أستغفرك وأتوب إليك) '' pak hai to aey Allah! aur sab tareef terey liye hai, main gawahi deta hun ke terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, main tujh sey maghfirat chahta hun aur teri taraf ruju karta hun'', to uski us majlis mein us sey honey wali khataaein maaf kar di jati hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, aur hum isey Suhel ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Barza aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3434,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki eik majlis mein majlis sey uthney sey pehley so so martaba : (رب اغفر لي وتب علي إنك أنت التواب الغفور) '' aey hamarey rab ! hamen bakhsh dey aur hamari tauba qubul farma , beshak to tauba qubul karney aur bakhshney wala hai'' , guna jata tha. Sufiyan ney Muhammad bin Suqa sey isi sanad key sath isi tarah usi key hum maana hadees riwayat ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3435,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam takleef key waqt ye dua padhtey they : (لا إله إلا الله الحليم الحكيم لا إله إلا الله رب العرش العظيم لا إله إلا الله رب السموات والأرض ورب العرش الكريم) ''koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai siwaye Allah buland o burdbar (samajhdar) key , aur koi mabood bar-haq nahin siwaye us Allah key jo arshe-azeem ka rab ( Malik ( hai aur koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai siwaye us Allah key jo aasmano aur zaminon ka rab hai aur qabiley-izzat arsh ka rab hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- hum sey bayan kya Muhammad bin Bashaar ney, wo kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kya ibne-abu-Adi ney, aur unhoney Hisham sey, Hisham ney Qatada sey, Qatada ney Abul-Aaliya sey, aur Abul-Aaliya ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mazkura riwayat key misl riwayat ki, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3436,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab kisi mushkil mamley sey do-chaar hotey to apna sar aasman ki taraf uthatey phir kehtey : «Subhanallahil-Azeem» '' Allah pak o bartar hai'' aur jab ji jaan laga kar dua kartey to kehtey : (يا حي يا قيوم) '' aey zinda zaat ! aey kaeynat ka nizam chalaney waley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib .
3437,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs kisi manzil par utrey aur ye dua padhey : (أعوذ بكلمات الله التامات من شر ما خلق) ''main Allah key mukammal kalimon key zariey Allah ki panah mein aata hun uski sari makhluqat key shar sey '', to jab tak ke wo apni us manzil sey kooch na karey usey koi chiz nuqsan na pahunchaeygi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- Malik bin Anas ney ye hadees is tarah riwayat ki ke unhen ye hadees Yaqub bin Abdullah bin Ashajj sey pahunchi hai, phir unhoney usi jaisi hadees bayan ki. (yani : Malik ney ye hadees balaghan riwayat ki hai) 3- ye hadees ibne-Ajlan sey bhi aai hai aur unhoney Yaqub bin Abdullah bin Ashajj sey riwayat ki hai, albatta unki riwayat mein (عن سعيد بن المسيب an خولة) hai, 4- Les ki hadees ibn Ajlan ki riwayat key muqabil mein ziyada sahih hai."
3438,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab safar par nikaltey aur apni sawari par sawar hotey to apni ungli sey aasman ki taraf ishara kartey huye kehtey : (اللهم أنت الصاحب في السفر والخليفة في الأهل اللهم اصحبنا بنصحك واقلبنا بذمة اللهم ازو لنا الأرض وهون علينا السفر اللهم إني أعوذ بك من وعثاء السفر وكآبة المنقلب)'' aey Allah ! tu hi rafeeq hai safar mein , aur tu hi khalifa hai ghar mein , ( meri adam mojudgi mein merey ghar ka dekh bhaal karney wala , naaib ( apni sari khairkhahiyon key sath hamarey sath mein reh, aur hamen apney thikaney par apni panah o hifazat mein lota ( wapis pahuncha), aey Allah ! to zamin ko hamarey liye samet dey aur safar ko aasan kar dey, aey Allah ! main safar ki mashaqqaton aur takleef sey teri panah chahta hun, aur panah maangta hun nakam o na-murad lotney key ranj o gham sey (ya lotney par ghar key badley huye burey haal sey) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- main usey nahin janta tha magar ibne-Abi Adi ki riwayat sey yahan tak ke Suwed ney mujh sey ye hadees ( aagey ki sanad sey) Suwed bin nasar kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kya Abdullah bin Mubarak ney , wo kehtey hain : hum sey Shoba ney isi sanad key sath isi tarah usi key hum maana hadees bayan ki padhi. , 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Shoba ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3439,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab safar kartey to kehtey : (اللهم أنت الصاحب في السفر والخليفة في الأهل اللهم اصحبنا في سفرنا واخلفنا في أهلنا اللهم إني أعوذ بك من وعثاء السفر وكآبة المنقلب ومن الحور بعد الكون ومن دعوة المظلوم ومن سوء المنظر في الأهل والمال)''aey Allah! to hamarey safar ka sathi hai, to hamarey peechey hamarey ehal o ayaal ka naaib o khalifa hai, aey Allah ! to hamarey sath reh hamarey us safar main to hamara naaib o khalifa bin ja hamarey ghar walon mein , aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun safar ki takleef o thakan sey aur nakam na-murad lotney key gham sey, aur mazloom ki bad dua sey aur maal aur ehale-khana mein waqey shuda kisi burey manzar sey (buri soorate-haal sey)''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- (الحور بعد الكون) ki jagah (الحور بعد الكور) bhi marvi hai, aur (الحور بعد الكور) ya (الحور بعد الكون) dono key maana eik hi hain, kehtey hain : uska maana ye hai ke panah maangta hun eman sey kufr ki taraf lotney sey ya taa'at sey ma'siyat ki taraf lotney sey , matlab ye hai ke us sey murad khair sey shar ki taraf lotna hai."
3440,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab safar sey wapis aatey to ye dua padhtey : (آيبون تائبون عابدون لربنا حامدون)''(hum salamti key sath safar sey) wapis aaney waley hain, hum (apney rab key huzur ( tauba karney waley hain, hum apney rab ki ibadat karney waley hain, aur hum apney rab key shukr guzar hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sory ney ye hadees Abu-Is'haq sey aur Abu-Is'haq ney Bara sey riwayat ki hai aur unhoney is hadees ki sanad mein Rabee ibn Bara ka zikr nahin kya hai, aur Shoba ki riwayat ziyada sahih o durust hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar, Anas aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3441,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab safar sey wapis laut'tey aur Madina ki diwarein dikhai deney lagtin to aap apni oontni ( sawari ( ko) apney watan ( Madina ki mohabbat mein tez daudaatey padhi. aur agar apni oontni key ilawa kisi aur sawari par hotey to usey bhi tez bhagatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3442,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab kisi shakhs ko rukhsat kartey to uska haath pakadtey padhi. aur uska haath us waqt tak na chhodtey jab tak ke wo shakhs khud hi aap ka haath na chhod deta aur aap kehtey : « استودع الله دينك وأمانتك وآخر عملك » ''main tera Deen , teri amanat , eman aur teri zindagi ka aakhiri amal ( sab ( Allah ki hawalgi aur sipurdagi mein deta hun''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey aai hai."
3443,"jab koi aadmi safar ka irada karta to ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma us sey kehtey : ''merey qarib aao main tumhen isi tarah sey al-wida kahunga jis tarah Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamen al-wada kehtey aur rukhsat kartey they, aap hamen rukhsat kartey waqt kehtey they : « أستودع الله دينك وأمانتك وخواتيم عملك » . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey jo Salim bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey aai hai Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3444,"eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! main safar par nikalney ka irada kar raha hun, to aap mujhey koi tosha dey dijiye , aap ney farmaya : '' Allah tujhey taqwa ka zaad safar dey'', usney kaha : mazeed izafa farma diijiye, aap ney farmaya : ''Allah tumharey gunah maaf kar dey'', usney kaha : mazeed kuch izafa farma dijiye, merey maa baap aap par qurban hun, aap ney farmaya : ''jahan kahin bhi tum raho Allah Taala tumharey liye khair (bhalai key kaam) aasan kar dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3445,"eik aadmi ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! main safar par nikalney ka irada kar raha hun to aap mujhey kuch wasiyat farma dijiye, aap ney farmaya : ''main tujhey Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karney ki wasiyat karta hun aur nasihat karta hun ke jahan kahin bhi unchaai o bulandi par chadho Allah ki takbir padho, ( Allahu-akbar kehtey raho ( phir jab aadmi palat kar safar par nikla to aap ney farmaya : « اللهم اطو له الأرض وهون عليه السفر » '' aey Allah ! uskey liye masafat ki doori ko lapet kar mukhtasar kar dey aur uskey liye safar ko aasan bana dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3446,"main Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas mojud tha, unhen sawari key liye eik chaupaya diya gaya, jab unhoney apna pair rikaab mein dala to kaha : « Bismillah » ''main Allah ka naam ley kar sawar ho raha hun '' aur phir jab peeth par jam kar beth gaey to kaha : «alhamdulillah» '' tamam tareefen Allah key liye hain'' , phir aap ney ye aayat : (سبحان الذي سخر لنا هذا وما كنا له مقرنين وإنا إلى ربنا لمنقلبون) ''pak hai wo zaat jisney usey hamarey qabu mein kya warna hum aisey na they jo usey nath pahna saktey, lagaam dey saktey, hum apney rab key paas palat kar janey waley hain'' , padhi, phir teen baar «alhamdulillah» kaha , aur teen baar (Allah akbar) kaha, phir ye dua padhi : (سبحانك إني قد zulmat نفسي فاغفر لي فإنه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت) ''pak hai to aey Allah ! beshak mainey apni jaan key haq mein zulm o ziyadti ki hai to mujhey bakhsh dey , kyonkey terey siwa koi zulm maaf karney wala nahin hai'' , phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hansey , mainey kaha : ameerul momeneen kis baat par aap hansey? unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha aap ney wesa hi kya jaisa mainey kya hai, phir aap hansey , mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! aap kis baat par hansey ? aap ney farmaya : '' tumhara rab apney bandey ki is baat sey khush hota hai jab wo kehta hai ke aey Allah merey gunah bakhsh dey kyonkey terey siwa koi aur zaat nahin hai jo gunahon ko maaf kar sakey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3447,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab safar farmatey to apni sawari par chadhtey aur teen baar (Allah akbar) kehtey . phir ye dua padhtey : (سبحان الذي سخر لنا هذا وما كنا له مقرنين وإنا إلى ربنا لمنقلبون) uskey baad aap ye dua padhtey : (اللهم إني أسألك في سفري هذا من البر والتقوى ومن العمل ما ترضى اللهم ہوں علينا المسير واطو عنا بعد الأرض اللهم أنت الصاحب في السفر والخليفة في الأهل اللهم اصحبنا في سفرنا واخلفنا في أهلنا)''aey Allah ! main apney is safar mein tujh sey neki aur taqwa ka Talib hun aur aisey amal ki tofiq maangta hun jis sey to razi ho, aey Allah to is safar ko aasan kar dey , zamin ki doori ko lapet kar hamarey liye kam kar dey , aey Allah to safar ka sathi hai, aur ghar mein) ghar walon ki dekh bhaal key liye ( mera naaib o qaaim maqam hai, aey Allah ! to hamarey sath hamarey safar mein reh , aur ghar walon mein hamari qaaim maqami farma'', aur aap jab ghar ki taraf palat'tey to kehtey they : (آيبون إن شاء الله تائبون عابدون لربنا حامدون) ''hum lotney waley hain apney ghar walon mein insha'Allah, tauba karney waley hain, apney rab ki ibadat karney waley hain, hamd bayan karney waley hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3448,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen tarah ki duayen maqbool hoti hain : mazloom ki dua, musafir ki dua, aur baap ki bad dua apney betey key haq mein ''."
3449,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab hawa chalti hui dekhtey to kehtey : (‏‏‏‏اللهم إني أسألك من خيرها وخير ما فيها وخير ما أرسلت به وأعوذ بك من شرها وشر ما فيها وشر ما أرسلت به) '' aey Allah ! main tujh sey uski khair maangta hun, aur jo khair is mein hai wo chahta hun aur jo khair uskey sath bheji gaee hai usey chahta hun, aur main uskey shar sey teri panah chahta hun aur jo shar is mein chupa huwa hai us sey panah maangta hun aur jo shar uskey sath bheji gaee hai us sey panah maangta hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Ubai-bin Kaab sey bhi riwayat hai aur ye hadees Hasan hai."
3450,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab bijli ki garaj aur kadak suntey to farmatey : (اللهم لا تقتلنا بغضبك wala تهلكنا بعذابك وعافنا قبل ذلك) ''aey Allah! to apney ghazab sey hamen na maar, apney azab key zariey hamen halak na kar , aur aisey burey waqt key aaney sey pehley hamen bakhsh dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3451,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab chaand dekhtey they to kehtey they : « اللهم أهلله علينا باليمن والإيمان والسلامة والإسلام ربي وربك الله » '' aey Allah ! Mubarak kar hamen ye chaand , barkat aur eman aur salamti aur Islam key sath , (aey chaand ! ( mera aur tumhara rab Allah hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3452,"do aadmiyon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney aapas mein gaali galoch kya un mein sey eik key chehrey sey ghussa dikh raha tha, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main eik aisa kalma janta hun ke agar wo us kalmey ko keh ley to uska ghussa kaafur ho jaey, wo kalma ye hai : (أعوذ بالله من الشيطان الرجيم) ''main Allah ki panah maangta hun raandey huye shetan sey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin sard sey bhi riwayat hai, aur ye hadees mursal (munqataa) hai."
3453,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey huye suna hai : tum mein sey jab koi achcha aur pasandida khuwab dekhey to samjhey ke ye Allah ki janib sey hai aur is par Allah ka shukr ada karey aur jo dekha ho usey logon sey bayan karey , aur jab kharab aur na-pasandida chizon mein sey koi chiz dekhey to samjhey ke ye shetan ki janib sey hai phir Allah sey uskey shar sey panah maangey aur kisi sey uska zikr na kerey. to ye chiz usey kuch nuqsan na pahunchaeygi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- ibne-haad ka naam Yazeed bin Abdullah bin Usama bin haad Madini hai aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa hain un sey Imam Malik aur doosrey logon ney riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3454,"log jab khajoor ka pehla phal dekhtey to usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ( tod kar) latey , jab usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam letey to farmatey (للهم بارك لنا في ثمارنا وبارك لنا في مدينتنا وبارك لنا في صاعنا ومدنا اللهم إن إبراهيم عبدك وخليلك ونبيك وإني عبدك ونبيك وإنه دعاك لمكة وأنا أدعوك للمدينة بمثل ما دعاك به لمكة ومثله) ''aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey phalon mein barkat dey, aur hamarey liye hamarey shehar mein barkat dey, hamarey saa mein barkat dey, hamarey mudd mein barkat dey, aey Allah ! Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) terey bandey hain, terey dost hain terey Nabi hain, aur main bhi tera banda aur tera Nabi hun, unhoney dua ki thi Makka key liye mein tujh sey dua karta hun Madina key liye , isi tarah ki dua jis tarah ki dua Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ney Makka key liye ki thi, balke uskey do gunaa ( barkat dey ( '' , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir aap ko jo koi chhota bacha nazar aata jata aap usey bulatey aur ye ( pehla ( phal usey dey detey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3455,"main aur Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu)) dono ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath ummul-momenin Memuna (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar mein dakhil huye, wo eik bartan ley kar hum logon key paas aain, us bartan mein doodh tha main aap key daain janib betha huwa tha aur Khalid aap key baain taraf they, aap ney doodh piya phir mujh sey farmaya : '' peeney ki baari to tumhari hai, lekin tum chaho to apna haq (apni baari ( Khalid bin Waleed ko dey do'', mainey kaha : aap ka jutha peeney mein apney aap par mein kisi ko tarjeeh nahin dey sakta , phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisey Allah khana khilaaey , usey kha kar ye dua padhni chahiye : « اللهم بارك لنا فيه وأطعمنا خيرا منه » '' aey Allah ! hamen is mein barkat aur mazeed us sey achcha khila'', aur jis ko Allah doodh pilaey usey kehna chahiye « اللهم بارك لنا فيه وزدنا منه » '' aey Allah ! hamen is mein barkat aur mazeed us sey achcha khula'', Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''doodh key siwa koi aisi chiz nahin hai jo khaney aur peeney (dono) ki jagah khaney o peeney ki zarurat puri kar sakey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney ye hadees Ali bin Zaid sey riwayat ki hai, aur unhoney umr bin hurmala kaha hai. jabke baaz ney umr bin hurmala kaha hai aur Amr bin hurmala kehna sahih nahin hai."
3456,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney sey jab dastar khuwan utha liya jata to aap kehtey : (الحمد لله حمدا كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه غير مودع wala مستغنى عنه ربنا) ''Allah hi key liye hain sari tareefen, bahut ziyada tareefen, pakizah rozi hai, ba-barkat rozi hai, ye Allah ki janib sey hamari aakhiri ghiza na ho aur aey hamarey rab hum us sey kabhi be niaz na hon''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3457,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab kha pi chuktey to kehtey : « الحمد لله الذي أطعمنا وسقانا وجعلنا مسلمين » '' sab taarifein us Allah key liye hain jisney hamen khilaya pilaya aur hamen musalman banaya''.
3458,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney khana khaya phir khaney sey farigh ho kar kaha : (الحمد لله الذي أطعمني هذا ورزقنيه من غير حول مني wala قوة غفر له ما تقدم من ذنبه) '' tamam tareefen hain us Allah key liye jisney hamen ye khana khilaya aur usey hamen ata kya, meri taraf sey mehnat mashaqqat aur jiddojehad aur quwat o taqat key istimal key baghair, to uskey agley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- aur abu marhoom ka naam abdur-Raheem bin Memun hai."
3459,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum murgh ki aawaz suno to Allah sey uska Fazal maango, kyonkey wo usi waqt boltaa hai jab usey koi farishta nazar aata hai, aur jab gadhey key renkney ki aawaz suno to shetan mardud sey Allah ki panah maango, kyonkey wo us waqt shetan ko dekh raha hota hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3460,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zameen par jo koi bhi banda : (لا إله إلا الله والله أكبر wala حول wala قوة إلا بالله) kaheyga ''Allah azz-w-jall key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai aur Allah Taala sab sey bada hai, aur Allah subhanahu o taala key siwa kisi kaam key karney ki kisi mein na koi taqat hai aur na hi quwat'', uskey (chhotey chhotey) gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey, agar-che samandar ki jhaag ki tarah (bahut ziyada) hun''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Shoba ney ye hadees isi sanad key sath isi tarah abu-balj sey riwayat ki hai, aur usey marfoo nahin kya, aur abu-balj ka naam Yahya bin abi Sulem hai aur unhen Yahya bin Sulem bhi kaha jata hai."
3461,"hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik ghazwey mein they, jab hum wapis paltey aur Madina key qarib pahunchey to logon ney takbir kahi aur buland aawaz sey kahi, aap ney farmaya : ''tumhara rab behra nahin hai aur na hi wo ghaaieb hai, wo tumharey darmiyan aur tumhari sawaariyon key darmiyan mojud hai, phir aap ney farmaya : ''Abdullah bin Qais! kya main tumhen jannat key khazanon mein sey eik khazana na bata dun? wo : (لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله) hai, yani harkat o quwat Allah Taala ki mashiyat key baghair nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Usman al-Nehdi ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin mul hai, 3- aur abu-Nuama ka naam Amr bin Esa hai, 4- aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol « بينكم وبين رءوس رحالكم » sey murad ye hai ke uska ilm aur qudrat har jagah hai."
3462,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis raat mujhey meraaj karaai gaee , us raat main Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) sey mila, Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : '' aey Muhammad ! apni ummat ko meri janib sey salam keh dena aur unhen bata dena ke jannat ki mitti bahut achi (zarkhez) hai, uska pani bahut mitha hai, aur wo khaali padi hui hai padhi. aur uski baghbani : (سبحان الله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر) sey hoti hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3463,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney hum-nasheen sey farmaya : ''kya tum mein sey koi is baat sey aajiz o nakam rahega ke eik din mein hazar nekiyan kama ley?'' aap key hum-nasheen mein sey eik poochhney waley ney puchha : hum mein sey koi kis tarah hazar nekiyan kamaeyga? aap ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey koi bhi so martaba tasbih padheyga ( yani subhan Allah ( to uskey liye hazar nekiyan likhi jaeyngi . aur uski hazar buraiyan mita di jaeyngi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3464,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney : (سبحان الله العظيم وبحمده) kaha , uskey liye jannat mein khajoor ka eik darkht laga diya jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, padhi. - aur hum isey sirf abu-Zubair ki riwayat sey jisey wo Jabir key wastey sey riwayat kartey hain jantey hain."
3465,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs : (سبحان الله العظيم وبحمده) kaheyga uskey liye jannat mein khajoor ka eik darkht lagaya jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3466,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs so baar : « سبحان وبحمده » kaheyga uskey gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey agar-che wo samandar ki jhaag ki tarah hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3467,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''do kalmey hain jo zaban par halkey hain (aasani sey ada ho jatey hain) magar meezaan mein bhari hain (tol mein wazni hain ( Rehman ko piyarey hain (wo ye hain) «سبحان وبحمده سبحان العظيم » . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3468,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney eik din mein so baar kaha : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو على كل شيء قدير) , to us ko das ghulam azad karney ka sawab hoga, aur uskey liye so nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, aur uski so buraiyan mita di jaeyngi, aur ye chiz uskey liye Sham tak shetan key shar sey bachaw ka zaria bin jaeygi, aur qiyamat key din koi us sey achcha amal ley kar na aayega siwaye us shakhs key jisney yehi amal us shakhs sey ziyada kya ho."
3469,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs subh o Sham mein so ( so ( martaba : « (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو على كل شيء قدير) وبحمده » kahey , qiyamat key din koi shakhs us sey achcha amal ley kar nahin aayega , siwaye us shakhs key jisney wohi kaha ho jo usney kaha hai ya us sey bhi ziyada usney ye dua padhi ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3470,"eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney Sahaba sey farmaya : سبحان الله وبحمده kaha karo, jisney ye kalma eik baar kaha uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jaeyngi , aur jisney das baar kaha uskey liye so nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, aur jisney so baar kaha uskey liye eik hazar nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, aur jo ziyada kaheyga Allah uski nekiyon mein bhi izafa farma dega, aur jo Allah sey bakhshish chahega Allah usko bakhsh dega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3471,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney so baar subh aur so baar Sham tasbih padhi ( yani « Subhanallah » kaha ( to wo so Haj kiye huye shakhs ki tarah ho jata hai. aur jisney so baar subh aur so baar Sham mein Allah ki hamd bayan ki) yani « Alhamdulillah » kaha ( usney to un fi sabeelillah ghaziyon ki sawaariyon key liye so ghodey faraham kiye ( Raavi ko shak ho gaya ye kaha ya ye kaha ( to usney so jihad kiye , aur jisney so baar subh aur so baar Sham ko Allah ki tahleel bayan ki) yani « la ilaha illa Allah » ( kaha to wo aisa ho jaeyga to un usney aulad Ismail mein sey so ghulam azad kiye aur jisney so baar subh aur so baar Sham ko (Allah akbar) kaha to qiyamat key din koi shakhs us sey ziyada nek amal ley kar hazir na hoga, siwaye uskey jisney us sey ziyada kaha hoga ya uskey barabar kaha hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3472,Ramzan main eik baar subhanallah kehna ghair Ramzan mein hazar baar Subhanallah kehney sey ziyada behtar hai.
3473,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs das martaba ( ye dua ) (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له إلها واحدا أحدا صمدا لم يتخذ صاحبة wala ولدا ولم يكن له كفوا أحد)''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah wahid key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, uska koi shareek nahin hai, wo tanha akela mabood hai, be niaz hai, usney na apna koi shareek hayaat banaya aur na hi uska koi beta hai, aur na hi koi uskey barabar hai'' , padhey to Allah Taala uskey liye chaar karod likhta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum us ko sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- khaleel bin Murra muhaddeseen key yahan qawi nahin hain aur Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke wo munkirul-hadees hain."
3474,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs namaz Fajr key baad jabke wo pair modey ( do zanu) betha huwa ho aur koi baat bhi na ki ho : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو على كل شيء) das martaba padhey to uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jaeyngi , aur uski das buraiyan mita di jaeyngi , uskey liye das darjey buland kiye jaeyngey aur wo us din purey din bhar har tarah ki makrooh o naa-pasandida chiz sey mehfooz rahega , aur shetan key zere-asar na aa paney key liye uski nigehbani ki jaeygi, aur koi gunah usey us din siwaye shirk-billah key halakat sey do-chaar na kar sakega. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3475,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko un kalmaat key sath : « اللهم إني أسألك بأني أشهد أنك أنت الله la إله إلا أنت الأحد الصمد الذي لم يلد ولم يولد ولم يكن له كفوا أحد » '' aey Allah ! main tujh sey maangta hun is taur par ke main tujhey gawah banata hun is baat par ke tu hi Allah hai, terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, to akela ( mabood ( hai to be-niyaz hai, ( to kisi ka mohtaj nahin terey sab mohtaj hain ( , ( to aisa be niaz hai) jisney na kisi ko jana hai aur na hi kisi ney isey jana hai, aur na hi koi uska hamsar huwa hai'' , dua kartey huye suna to farmaya : '' qism hai us rab ki jis key qabzey mein meri jaan hai ! us shakhs ney Allah sey uskey us Isme-Aazma key waseeley sey manga hai ke jab bhi uskey zariey dua ki gaee hai usney wo dua qubul ki hai, aur jab bhi uskey zariey koi chiz maangi gaee hai usney di hai ''. Zaid ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : mainey ye hadees kaee barson baad zuhair bin Muawiya sey zikr ki to unhoney kaha ke mujh sey ye hadees Abu-Is'haq ney Malik bin mighwal key wastey sey bayan ki hai. Zaid kehtey hain : phir mainey ye hadees Sufiyan Sory sey zikr ki to unhoney mujh sey ye hadees Malik key wastey sey bayan ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- shareek ney ye hadees Abu-Is-haq sey , Abu-Is-haq ney ibn Barida sey , ibne-Barida ney apney walid ( Barida (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat ki hai, halanke Abu-Is'haq Hamdani ney ye hadees Malik bin mighwal sey riwayat ki hai."
3476,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hum logon key sath ( masjid mein) tashrif farma they, us waqt eik shakhs masjid mein aaya , usney namaz padhi , aur ye dua ki : aey Allah ! meri maghfirat kar dey aur mujh par reham farma , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aey namazi ! tu ney jaldi ki, jab to namaz padh kar bethey to Allah key shayaane-shaan uski hamd bayan kar aur phir mujh par salaat ( durood ( bhej , phir Allah sey dua kar '' , kehtey hain : uskey baad phir eik aur shakhs ney namaz padhi , usney Allah ki hamd bayan ki aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par durood bheja to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aey namazi ! dua kar , teri dua qubul ki jaeygi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- is hadees ko Hewa bin Shureh ney abu-Haani khaulaani sey riwayat ki hai."
3477,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko namaz key andar padhi. dua kartey huye suna , usney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par salaat ( durood ( na bheja , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' usney jaldi ki '' , phir aap ney usey bulaya , aur us sey aur uskey ilawa dusron ko khitab kar key farmaya , '' jab tum mein sey koi bhi namaz padh chukey padhi. to usey chahiye ke wo pehley Allah ki hamd o sana bayan karey , phir Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par salaat ( durood ( bhejey , phir uskey baad wo jo chahey dua maangey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3478,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ka Isme-Azam un do aayaton mein hai) eik aayat ) (وإلهكم إله واحد لا إله إلا هو الرحمن الرحيم)  '' tum sab ka mabood eik hi mabood bar-haq hai, uskey siwa koi mabood nahin hai, wo Rehman , Rahim hai'' ( Baqra : 163) , aur) dusri aayat ( Aale-Imran ki shuru ki aayat (الم الله لا إله إلا هو الحي القيوم)  hai'' « Alif-Lam-Mim » , padhi. Allah Taala wo hai jis key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, jo « hayi » zinda aur « qayyum » sab ka nigehban hai'' ( Aale-Imran : 1- padhi. ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3479,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum Allah sey dua maango aur us yaqin key sath maango ke tumhari dua zarur qubul hogi , aur) achi tarah ( jaan lo ke Allah Taala be-parwai aur be-tawajjahi sey maangi hui ghaflat aur lahu w laib mein mubtala dil ki dua qubul nahin karta ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- mainey Abbas anbarii ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Abdullah bin Muawiya jamhi ki bayan karda riwaayatein likh lo kyonkey wo Suqa Raavi hain."
3480,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kehtey they : (اللهم عافني في جسدي وعافني في بصري واجعله الوارث مني لا إله إلا الله الحليم الكريم سبحان الله رب العرش العظيم والحمد لله رب العالمين) '' aey Allah ! to mujhey merey jism mein aafiyat ata kar) yani mujhey sehat dey (aur mujhey aafiyat dey meri nigahon mein) yani meri beenai sahih Salim rakh (aur usey ( yani meri nigah ko) aakhiri waqt tak ( yani basaarat ko baqi o qaaim rakh chahey aur kisi chiz mein kamzori aur zawal aa jaey to aa jaey) koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai siwaye Allah key jo halim aur karim hai, pak hai Allah arsh azeem wala aur tamam tarifen us Allah key hain jo sarey jahan ka rab hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Habib bin abi Sabit ney Urwa bin Zuber sey kuch bhi nahin suna hai, Allah behtar janta hai."
3481,"Fatima ( bint Rasool ( (Raziallahu Anha) aap key paas eik khadim maangney aain, aap ney unsey kaha : tum ye dua padhti raho : (اللهم رب السموات السبع ورب العرش العظيم ربنا ورب كل شيء منزل التوراة والإنجيل والقرآن فالق الحب والنوى أعوذ بك من شر كل شيء أنت آخذ بناصيته أنت الأول فليس قبلك شيء وأنت الآخر فليس بعدك شيء وأنت الظاهر فليس فوقك شيء وأنت الباطن فليس دونك شيء اقض عني الدين وأغنني من الفقر)'' aey Allah ! to saton aasmano ka rab , arshe-azeem ka rab , aey hamarey rab ! aur har chiz key rab , Torat, Injeel aur Quran key nazil karney waley , zamin phaad kar daney uganey aur akhwey nikalney waley, main teri panah chahta hun har chiz key shar sey , jiski peshani terey haath mein hai, to pehla hai) shuru sey hai) tujh sey pehley koi chiz nahin hai, to sab sey aakhir hai terey baad koi chiz nahin, to sab sey zahir (yani ooper hai) , terey ooper koi chiz nahin hai, to poshida hai sab ki nazron sey , lekin tum sey koi chiz poshida nahin hai, aey Allah ! to merey ooper sey qarz utaar dey, aur mujhey mohtaji sey nikal kar maaldar kar dey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur Aamash key baaz shagirdon ney Aamash sey aisey hi riwayat ki hai, 2- aisey hi baaz raawiyon ney Aamash sey , Aamash ney abu-Saaleh sey mursal tareeqey sey riwayat ki hai, aur unhoney apni riwayat mein Abu-Hurera ka zikr nahin kya hai."
3482,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye dua padhtey they : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من قلب لا يخشع ومن دعا لا يسمع ومن نفس لا تشبع ومن علم لا ينفع أعوذ بك من هؤلاء الأربع) '' aey Allah ! main teri panah maangta hun aisey dil sey jo darta na ho ( yani jis mein khofe-Ilaahi na ho) , aur aisi dua sey bhi teri panah maangta hun jo suni na jaey, aur us nafs sey bhi teri panah maangta hun jo sair na ho, aur aisey ilm sey bhi teri panah chahta hun jo faeyda na pahunchaey, aey Allah! main un chaaron chizon sey teri panah chahta hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey) yani ( Abdullah bin Amr ki riwayat Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3483,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey baap sey puchha : ''aey Husain ! aaj kal tum kitney mabudon ko pujtey ho?'' merey baap ney jawab diya saat ko chhe zamin mein) rehtey hain (aur eik aasman mein , aap ney puchha : '' un mein sey kis ki sab sey ziyada raghbat dilchaspi , ummid aur khof o dar key sath ibadat kartey ho? '' unhoney kaha : uski jo aasman mein hai, aap ney farmaya : '' aey Husain! suno , agar tum Islam ley aatey to main tumhen do kalmey sikha deta wo dono tumhen barabar nafa pahunchatey rehtey '' , phir jab Husain Islam ley aaye to unhoney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey wo dono kalmey sikha dijiye jinhen sikhaaney ka aap ney mujh sey wada farmaya tha, aap ney farmaya : '' kaho (اللهم ألهمني رشدي وأعذني من شر نفسي) '' aey Allah ! to mujhey meri bhalai ki baaten sikha dey , aur merey nafs key shar sey mujhey bacha ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees Imran bin Husain sey is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai."
3484,"mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aksar o beshtar un alfaz sey dua maangtey sunta tha : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الهم والحزن والعجز والكسل والبخل وضلع الدين وغلبة الرجال) '' aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun fikr w gham sey , aajizi sey aur kaahili sey aur bakheeli sey aur qarz key ghalbey sey aur logon key qehar o zulm o ziyadti sey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey yani Amr bin abi Amr ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3485,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye dua kartey they : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الكسل والهرم والجبن والبخل وفتنة المسيح وعذاب القبر) '' aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun susti o kahili sey , aur intehai budhapey sey) jis mein aadmi hosh o hawaas kho bethta hai) buzdili o kanjusi sey aur Masih ( dajjaal ( key fitna sey aur azabe-qabr sey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3486,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko tasbih ka shumar apney haath ki ungliyon par kartey huye dekha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, yani Aamash ki riwayat sey jisey wo Ata bin Saaib sey riwayat kartey hain, padhi. - Shoba aur Sory ney ye puri hadees Ata bin Saaib sey riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Yusera bint Yasir (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey huye kehti hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aey aurton ki jamaat ! tum tasbeehaat ka shumar ungliyon key poron sey kar liya karo, kyonkey un sey puchha jaeyga aur unhen goyai ata ki jaeygi ''."
3487,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik Sabab ki jo bimari sey sakht laaghar aur sookh kar chidiya key bachey ki tarah ho gaey they iyaadat ki, aap ney un sey farmaya : '' kya tum apney rab sey apni sehat o aafiyat ki dua nahin kartey they?'' unhoney kaha : main dua karta tha ke aey Allah ! jo saza to mujhey aakhirat mein deney wala tha wo saza mujhey to duniya hi mein pehley hi dedey , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' subhan Allah ! pak hai Allah ki zaat , to us saza ko kaatney aur jhelney ki taqat o istataat nahin rakhta , tum ye kyon nahin kaha kartey they : '' aey Allah ! to hamen duniya mein bhi neki , achai o bhalai dey aur aakhirat mein bhi Hasna , neki bhalai o achai dey , aur bacha ley to hamen jahannam key azab sey '' ( Baqra : 201) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- ye hadees Anas bin Malik key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey deegar kaee aur sanadon sey bhi aai hai."
3488,"Allah Taala ki us aayat : « ربنا آتنا في الدنيا حسنة وفي الآخرة حسنة » key barey mein Hasan sey marvi hai, duniya mein « Hasna » sey murad ilm aur ibadat hai, aur aakhirat mein « Hasna » sey murad jannat hai."
3489,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye dua kartey they : « اللهم إني أسألك الهدى والتقى والعفاف والغنى » '' aey Allah ! main tujh sey hidayat ka Talib hun, taqwa ka talabgar hun, pakdamni ka khaahishmand hun, maldari aur be niazi chahta hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3490,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki duaon mein sey eik dua ye thi : (اللهم إني أسألك حبك وحب من يحبك والعمل الذي يبلغني حبك اللهم اجعل حبك أحب إلي من نفسي وأهلي ومن الماء البارد)''aey Allah ! main tujh sey teri mohabbat maangta hun, aur main us shakhs ki bhi tujh sey mohabbat maangta hun jo tujh sey mohabbat karta hai, aur aisa amal chahta hun jo mujhey teri mohabbat tak pahuncha dey , aey Allah ! to apni mohabbat ko mujhey meri jaan aur merey ghar walon sey ziyada mehbub bana dey , aey Allah ! apni mohabbat ko thandey pani ki mohabbat sey bhi ziyada kar dey '' , ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka zikr kartey to unkey barey mein batatey huye kehtey : wo logon mein sab sey ziyada ibadat guzar they."
3491,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni dua mein kehtey they : (اللهم ارزقني حبك وحب من ينفعني حبه عندك اللهم ما رزقتني مما أحب فاجعله قوة لي فيما تحب اللهم وما زويت عني مما أحب فاجعله فراغا لي فيما تحب)'aey Allah ! to mujhey apni mohabbat ata kar , aur mujhey us shakhs ki bhi mohabbat ata kar jiski mohabbat mujhey terey darbar mein faeyda dey , aey Allah ! jo bhi to mujhey meri pasandida o pakizah rizq ata karey us rizq ko apni pasandida chizon mein istimal key liye quwat o taqat ka zaria bana dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3492,"mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi aisa taaweez ( panah leney ki dua ( sikha dijiye jisey padh kar mein Allah ki panah hasil kar liya karun, to aap ney mera kandha pakda aur kaha : kaho ( padho ( : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من شر سمعي ومن شر بصري ومن شر لساني ومن شر قلبي ومن شر منيي يعني فرجه)'' aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun apney kaan key shar sey , apni aankh key shar sey , apni zaban key shar sey , apney dil key shar sey , aur apni sharmgaah key shar sey '' ( mani sey murad sharmgaah hai) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad yani « Saad bin Aus an Bilal bin Yahya» key tareeq sey jantey hain."
3493,"mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key pehlu mein soi hui thi, raat mainey aap ko apni jagah na paa kar aap ko idhar-udhar talash kya, tatola, mera haath aap key qadmon par pada , us waqt aap sajdey mein they, aur ye dua padh rahey they : (أعوذ برضاك من سخطك وبمعافاتك من عقوبتك لا أحصي ثناء عليك أنت كما أثنيت على نفسك) '' aey Allah ! main teri raza o khushnudi key zariey teri narazagi sey panah maangta hun, aur terey afu dar-guzar key saharey teri saza o azab sey panah maangta hun, main teri sana, teri tareef ki ginti aur uska Ihata nahin kar sakta, to wesa hi hai jaisa ke tu ney khud aap apni zaat ki tareef ki hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey aai hai."
3494,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unhen ( Sahaba ko) ye dua sikhaya kartey they jaisa ke unhen Quran ki sura sikhaya kartey they : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من عذاب جهنم ومن عذاب القبر وأعوذ بك من فتنة المسيح الدجال وأعوذ بك من فتنة المحيا والممات) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun jahannam key azab sey aur qabr key azab sey aur main teri panah chahta hun Masih dajjaal key fitna sey, aur main teri panah chahta hun hayaat o maut key fitney (kash-m-kash ( sey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3495,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam un kalmaat key zariey dua farmaya kartey they : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من فتنة النار وعذاب النار وفتنة القبر وعذاب القبر ومن شر فتنة الغنى ومن شر فتنة الفقر ومن شر فتنة المسيح الدجال اللهم اغسل خطاياي بماء الثلج والبرد وأنق قلبي من الخطايا كما أنقيت الثوب الأبيض من الدنس وباعد بيني وبين خطاياي كما باعدت بين المشرق والمغرب اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الكسل والهرم والمأثم والمغرم)''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun jahannam key fitney sey , ( jahannam mein ley janey waley aamal sey) jahannam key azab sey aur qabr key azab sey , aur qabr key fitney sey, (munkar nakeer key sawal sey jiska jawab na padey) maldari key fitney key shar sey (takabbur aur haram kamai sey (aur mohtaji key fitney key shar sey, (hasad aur tamaa (lalach) sey) aur Masih dajjaal key shar sey, aey Allah ! hamarey gunahon ko dhul dey barf aur olon key pani sey, aur merey dil ko gunahon sey saaf kar dey jis tarah ke to safed kapda mail kuchail sey saaf karta hai, aur merey aur merey gunahon key darmiyan itni doori paida kar dey jitni doori tu ney mashriq aur maghrib key darmiyan paida kar di hai, aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun kaahili sey, budhapey sey, gunah sey aur tawaan o qarz key bojh sey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3496,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aap ki wafat key waqt ( ye dua ( padhtey huye suna hai : « اللهم اغفر لي وارحمني وألحقني بالرفيق الأعلى » '' aey Allah ! bakhsh dey mujh ko aur reham farma mujh par aur mujh ko rafeeqe-Aala (anbiya o malaaika) sey mila dey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3497,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (koi shakhs dua maangey to) is tarah na kahey : '' aey Allah ! to chahey to hamen bakhsh dey , aey Allah ! to chahey to hum par reham farma '' padhi. balke zor daar tareeqey sey maangey , isliye ke Allah ko koi majbur karney wala to hai nahin (ke kaha jaey : agar to chahey ( , Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3498,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' hamara rab har raat aasmane-duniya par aakhiri tihai raat mein utarta hai aur kehta hai : ''kon hai jo mujhey pukarey ke main uski dua qubul kar lun? kon hai jo mujh sey maangey ke main usey ata kar dun? aur kon hai jo mujh sey maghfirat maangey ke main usey bakhsh dun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai 2- aur abu-Adbullah al-Agharr ka naam Salman hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Ali , Abdullah bin Masood, abu-Saeed , Juber bin Mut-im , Rifa Johni, abu-Darda aur Usman bin abul-Aas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayatein hain."
3499,"puchha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon si dua ziyada suni jati hai? aap ney farmaya : ''aadhi raat key aakhir ki dua ( yani tihai raat mein maangi hui dua (aur farz namazon key akheer mein '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Abu-Zar aur ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain ke aap ney farmaya : ''raat key aakhiri hissey mein dua sab sey behtar hai, ya uskey qubul honey ki umeeden ziyada hain ya usi jaisi koi aur baat aap ney farmaey''."
3500,"eik shakhs ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey aaj raat aap ki dua suni , mainey aap ki jo dua suni wo ye thi : (اللهم اغفر لي ذنبي ووسع لي في داري وبارك لي فيما رزقتني) '' aey Allah ! merey gunah bakhsh dey aur merey ghar mein kushadgi dey , aur merey rizq mein barkat dey'' , aap ney farmaya : '' kya un dua'aiya kalmaat ney kuch chhoda? (yani un mein Deen duniya ki sabhi bhalaiyan aa gaee hain). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3501,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs subh mein ye kalmaat kaheyga : (اللهم أصبحنا نشهدك ونشهد حملة عرشك وملائكتك وجميع خلقك بأنك الله لا إله إلا أنت الله وحدك لا شريك لك وأن محمدا عبدك ورسولك) ''aey Allah! hamney subh ki aur hum tujhey gawah banatey hain aur tera arsh uthaey rehney walon , terey farishton ko teri sari makhluqat ko gawah bana kar kehtey hain ke tu hi Allah hai terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, to akela Allah hai tera koi shareek nahin hai, aur Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam terey bandey aur terey Rasool hain'', to us din us sey jitney bhi gunah hongey unhen Allah bakhsh dega aur agar wo ye dua Sham key waqt padheyga to us raat us sey jitney bhi gunah sarzad hongey Allah unhen bakhsh dega . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3502,"kam hi aisa hota ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni kisi majlis sey apney Sahaba key liye ye dua kiye baghair uthey hun : (اللهم اقسم لنا من خشيتك ما يحول بيننا وبين معاصيك ومن طاعتك ما تبلغنا به جنتك ومن اليقين ما تهون به علينا مصيبات الدنيا ومتعنا بأسماعنا وأبصارنا وقوتنا ما أحييتنا واجعله الوارث منا واجعل ثأرنا على من ظلمنا وانصرنا على من عادانا wala تجعل مصيبتنا في ديننا wala تجعل الدنيا أكبر همنا wala مبلغ علمنا wala تسلط علينا من لا يرحمنا)''aey Allah! hamarey darmiyan to apna itna khof baant dey jo hamarey aur hamarey gunahon key darmiyan haael ho jaey, aur hamarey darmiyan apni itaat o farmanbradri ka itna jazba phela dey jo hamen teri jannat tak pahuncha dey, aur hamen itna yaqin dedey jis key saharey duniya ki museebatein heech aur aasan ho jaeyn, aur jab tak to zinda rakh hamen apney kanon apni aakhon aur apni quwaton sey faeyda uthaney ki tofiq deta reh, aur un sab ko (hamari maut tak) baqi rakh, aur hamara qisaas aur hamara badla un sey ley jo hum par zulm karey , aur jo hum sey dushmani karey uskey muqabil mein hamari madad farma , aur duniya ko hamara bura maqsad na bana dey , aur na hamarey ilm ki inteha bana (ke hamara sara seekhna sikhana sirf duniya ki khatir ho (aur hum par kisi aisey shakhs ko musallat na kar jo hum par reham na karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, baaz muhaddeseen ney ye hadees Khalid bin abu-Imraan sey aur Khalid ney Nafey key wastey sey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai."
3503,"merey baap ney mujhey : (لا إله إلا الله العلي العظيم لا إله إلا الله الحليم الكريم لا إله إلا الله سبحان الله رب العرش العظيم) '' aey Allah main gham o fikr aur susti o kahili aur azabe-qabr sey teri panah chahta hun '' , padhtey huye suna to kaha : aey betey tu ney ye dua kis sey suni ? mainey kaha : mainey aap ko ye dua padhtey huye suni hai, unhoney kaha : unhen pabandi sey padhtey raha karo, isliye ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye dua padhtey huye suna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3504,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : '' kya main tum ko aisey kalmaat na sikha dun ke un kalmaat ko jab tum kaho gey to tumharey gunah Allah Taala maaf farma dega , agar-che tum un logon mein sey ho jinkey gunah pehley hi maaf kiye ja chukey hain'' , aap ney farmaya : '' kaho :(لا إله إلا الله العلي العظيم لا إله إلا الله الحليم الكريم لا إله إلا الله سبحان الله رب العرش العظيم)  '' Allah jo buland o baala hai, uskey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, haleem o karim (burdbar (samajhdar) meharban ( Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, koi mabood nahin siwaye Allah key , pak hai Allah jo arsh azeem ka rab hai ''."
3505,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' zun-noon( Yunus (Alaihissalam) ( ki dua jo unhoney machli key pet mein rehney key doran ki thi wo ye thi : (لا إله إلا أنت سبحانك إني كنت من الظالمين)  '' terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, Tu Pak hai, main hi zalim ( khatakar ( hun '' , kyonkey ye aisi dua hai ke jab bhi koi musalman shakhs usey padh kar dua kerega to Allah Taala uski dua qubul farmaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muhammad bin Yahya ney kaha : Muhammad bin Yusuf kabhi Ibrahim bin Muhammad bin Saad key wastey sey Saad sey riwayat kartey hain aur is mein « an Abeeh » ka zikr nahin kartey , 2- doosrey raawiyon ney ye hadees Yunus bin Abu-Is-haq sey , aur Yunus ney Ibrahim bin Muhammad bin Saad key wastey sey Saad sey riwayat ki hai, aur us riwayat mein unhoney « an Abeeh » ka zikr nahin kya hai, padhi. - baaz ney Yunus bin Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat ki hai, aur un logon ney ibn Yusuf ki riwayat ki tarah Ibrahim bin Muhammad bin Saad sey riwayat kartey huye « an Abeeh an Saad » kaha hai aur Yunus bin Abu-Is'haq ki aadat thi ke kabhi to wo is hadees mein « an Abeeh » keh kar riwayat kartey aur kabhi « an Abeeh » ka zikr nahin kartey they."
3506,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key ninnanwey padhi. naam hain, so main eik kam , jo unhen yad rakhey wo jannat mein dakhil hoga '' padhi. ."
3507,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key ninnanwey ( 99 ( naam hain jo unhen shumar karey ( giney ( ga wo jannat mein jaeyga, aur Allah key ninnanwey ( 99 ( naam ye hain : « الله » Ism zaat sab namon sey ashraf o aalaa , « الرحمن » '' bahut reham karney wala '' , « الرحيم » '' meharban '' , « الملك » '' badshah '' , « القدوس » '' nihayat pak '' , « السلام » '' salamti deney wala '' , « المؤمن » '' yaqin wala '' , « المهيمن » '' nigehban '' , « العزيز » '' ghalib '' , « الجبار » '' tasallut wala '' , « المتكبر » '' badai wala '' , « الخالق » '' paida karney wala '' , « البارئ » '' paida karney wala '' , « المصور » '' surat bananey wala '' , « الغفار » '' bahut bakhshney wala , « القهار » '' qehar wala '' , « الوهاب » '' bahut deney wala '' , « الرزاق » '' rozi deney wala '' , « الفتاح » '' faisla chukaney wala '' , « العليم » '' janney wala '' , « القابض » '' rokney wala '' , « الباسط » '' chhod deney wala , phelaney wala '' , « الخافض » '' past karney wala '' , « الرافع » '' buland karney wala '' , « المعز » '' izzat deney wala '' , « المذل » '' zillat deney wala '' , « السميع » '' sunney wala '' , « البصير » '' dekhney wala '' , « الحكم » '' faisla karney wala '' , « العدل » '' insaf wala '' , « اللطيف » '' bandon par shafqat karney wala '' , « الخبير » '' khabar rakhney wala '' , « الحليم » '' burdbar (samajhdar) '' , « العظيم » '' buzurgi wala '' , « الغفور » '' bahut bakhshney wala '' , « الشكور » '' qadr karney wala '' , « العلي » '' ooncha '' , « الكبير » '' bada '' , « الحفيظ » '' nigehban '' , « المقيت » '' taqat o quwat wala '' , « الحسيب » '' hisab leney wala '' , « الجليل » '' buzurg '' , « الكريم » '' karam wala '' , « الرقيب » '' muttala rehney wala '' , « المجيب » '' qubul karney wala '' , « الواسع » '' kushadgi aur wusat wala '' , « الحكيم » '' hikmat wala '' , « الودود » '' bahut chahney wala '' , « المجيد » '' buzurgi wala '' , « الباعث » '' zinda kar key uthaney wala '' , « الشهيد » '' nigran , hazir '' , « الحق » '' sacha '' , « الوكيل » '' karsaz '' , « القوي » '' taqatwar '' , « المتين » '' mazbut '' , « الولي » '' madadgar o muhafiz '' , « الحميد » , padhi. « المحصي » , padhi. « المبدئ » '' pehley pehal paida karney wala '' , « المعيد » '' dobara paida karney wala '' , « المحيي » '' zinda karney wala '' , « المميت » '' maarney wala '' , « الحي » '' zinda '' , « القيوم » '' qaaim rehney o qaaim rakhney wala '' , « الواجد » '' paney wala '' , « الماجد » '' buzurgi wala '' , « الواحد » '' akela '' , « الصمد » '' be niaz '' , « القادر » '' qudrat wala '' , « المقتدر » '' taqatwar pakadney wala '' , « المقدم » '' pehla '' , « المؤخر » '' pichhlaa '' , « الأول » '' pehla '' , « الآخر » '' pichhlaa '' , « الظاهر » '' zahir '' , « الباطن » '' poshida , makhfii '' , « الوالي » '' Malik mukhtaar , hukumat karney wala '' , « المتعالي » '' bartar '' , « البر » '' bhalai wala '' , « التواب » '' tauba qubul karney wala '' , « المنتقم » '' intiqam leney wala '' , « العفو » '' darguzar karney wala '' , « الرءوف » '' shafqat wala , meharban '' , « maalik الملك » '' tamam jahan ka Malik '' , « ذو الجلال والإكرام » '' izzat o jalal wala '' , « المقسط » '' insaf karney wala '' , « الجامع » '' jama karney wala '' , « الغني » ''tawangar o beniyaz '' , « المغني » '' be niyaz '' , « المانع » '' rokney wala '' , « الضار » '' nuqsan pahunchane-wala '' , « النافع » '' nafa pahunchane-wala '' , « النور » '' roshan , zahir '' , « الهادي » '' hidayat bakhshney wala '' , « البديع » '' naey sirey sey paida karney wala '' , « الباقي » '' qaaim rehney wala '' , « الوارث » '' waris '' , « الرشيد » '' khair o bhalai wala '' , « الصبور » '' burdbar (samajhdar) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum sey kaee raawiyon ney ye hadees Safwan bin abu-Saaleh key wastey sey bayan ki hai, aur ye hadees hum sirf Safwan bin Saleh ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Safwan bin Saleh muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa hain, 3- ye hadees kaee aur sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai, aur hum aksar o beshtar riwayaat ko jin mein Asmae-Ilaahi ka zikr hai, is hadees key siwa kisi hadees ko sanad key aetbar sey sahih nahin paatey, 4- Adam ibne-Abi Ayas ney ye hadees is sanad key ilawa do sarii sanad sey Abu-Hurera sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai aur is mein Asmae-Ilaahi ka zikr kya hai, lekin is hadees ki sanad sahih nahin hai."
3508,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key ninnanwey ( 99 ( naam hain jisney unhen shumar kya ( yad rakha ( wo jannat mein jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is hadees mein Asma ( Ilahi (ka zikr nahin hai, 3- usey Abul-Yaman ney Shuaib bin abi Hamza key wastey sey abu-Zinad sey riwayat kya hai aur is mein Asmaye Husna ka zikr nahin kya."
3509,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum jannat key baaghon mein sey kisi baagh key paas sey guzro to kuch char-chug liya karo'', main puchha : Allah key Rasool ! « رياض الجنة » kya hai? aap ney farmaya : '' « رياض الجنة » masaajid hain'' , mainey kaha aur « الرتع » kya hai, aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : '' سبحان الله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر kehna « الرتع » hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3510,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum jannat key baaghon sey guzro to tum ( kuch ( char , chug liya karo padhi. logon ney puchha « رياض الجنة » kya hai? aap ney farmaya : '' zikr key halqey aur zikr ki majlisen ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey jisey Sabit ney Anas sey riwayat ki hai Hasan gharib hai."
3511,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey kisi ko koi musibat laahiq ho to usey : إنا لله وإنا إليه راجعون اللهم عندك احتسبت مصيبتي فأجرني فيها وأبدلني منها خيرا'' hum sab Allah key liye hain aur hum Allah hi ki taraf lot kar janey waley hain, aey Allah ! main apni musibaton ka ajr tujh sey chahta hun mujhey to un par) sabr karney ka ( achcha ajr dey , aur un musibaton key badley mujhey un sey achcha dey '' , padhna chahiye, phir jab abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut ka waqt aa gaya to unhoney dua ki : « اللهم اخلف في أهلي خيرا مني » '' aey Allah ! merey ghar walon mein mujh sey behtar zaat ko mera khalifa o jaa-nashin bana dey'', aur jab unki maut waqey ho gaee to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : إنا لله وإنا إليه راجعون عند الله احتسبت مصيبتي فأجرني فيها. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai 3- aur abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam Abdullah bin Abdul-Asad hai."
3512,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! kon si dua afzal ( sab sey achi ( hai? aap ney farmaya : '' apney rab sey duniya o aakhirat mein balaaon o musibaton sey bacha deney ki dua karo '' , phir aap key paas wohi shakhs doosrey din bhi aaya , aur aap sey phir puchha : '' kon si dua afzal hai? '' aap ney isey wesa hi jawab diya jaisa pehley jawab diya tha, wo shakhs teesrey din bhi aap key paas hazir huwa , us din bhi aap ney usey wesa hi jawab diya, mazeed farmaya : '' jab tumhen duniya o aakhirat mein aafiyat mil jaey to samajh lo ke tum ney kamiyabi hasil kar li''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Salma bin Wardan ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3513,"mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! agar mujhey malum ho jaey ke kon si raat Leilatul-Qadr hai to main is mein kya padhun? aap ney farmaya : ''padho « اللهم إنك afu كريم تحب العفو فاعف عني » '' aey Allah ! to afu o darguzar karney wala meharban hai, aur afu o darguzar karney ko to pasand karta hai, isliye to hamen maaf o darguzar kar dey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3514,"mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi aisi chiz sikhaaiye jisey main Allah rabbul-Izzat sey maangta rahun, aap ney farmaya : ''Allah sey aafiyat maango'', phir kuch din ruk kar main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hazir huwa aur arz kya : mujhey koi aisi chiz bataiye jisey main Allah sey maangta rahun, aap ney farmaya : ''aey Abbas ! aey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key chacha ! duniya o aakhirat mein aafiyat talab karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- Abdullah bin Haris bin naufal ney Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai (yani unka un sey samaa, Sabit hai) ."
3515,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah sey jo bhi cheezen maangi gaee hain un mein Allah ko sab sey ziyada pasand ye hai ke us sey aafiyat ( duniya o aakhirat ki musibaton sey najat ( maangi jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- aur hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Bakar Muleki ki riwayat sey jantey hain, (aur ye zaeef hain ( ."
3516,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab kisi kaam ka irada kartey to ye dua farmatey : « اللهم خر لي واختر لي » '' aey Allah ! merey liye behtar ka intikhaab farma aur merey liye behtar pasand farma ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai 2- aur hum usey Zanfal ki riwayat key siwa aur kisi sanad sey nahin jantey , aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, aur unhen Zanfal bin Abdullah Urfi bhi kehtey hain, wo Arafat mein rehtey they, wo is hadees mein munfarid hain, yani ye riwayat sirf unhoney hi bayan ki hai) kisi aur ney nahin (aur kisi ney bhi un ki mutaabiat nahin ki hai."
3517,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wuzu aadha eman hai, aur « الحمد لله » ( Allah ki hamd ( meezaan ko sawab sey bhar dega aur « Subhanallah » aur « الحمد لله » ye dono bhar dengey aasmano aur zamin key darmiyan ki jagah ko ya un mein sey har eik bhar dega aasmano aur zamin key darmiyan ki sari khala ko) ajr o sawab sey) « صلاة » Noor hai, aur « صدقة » daleel aur kasoti hai) eman ki (aur « sabr » roshni hai aur « Quran » tumharey haq mein hujjat o daleel hai ya aur tumharey khilaf hujjat hai. har insan subh uth kar apney nafs ko farokht karta hai chunanche ya to ( Allah key yahan farokht kar key (us ko) jahannam sey) azad kara leta hai, ya (shetan key yahan farokht kar key (us ko halakat mein dal deta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3518,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' « تسبيح » ( subhan Allah kehney sey) nisf meezaan ( aadha paldaa ( bhar jaeyga, aur « الحمد لله » meezaan ( paldey key baqi khaali hissey ( ko pura bhar dega , aur « لا إله إلا الله » key to Allah tak pahunchney mein koi hijaab o rukawat hai hi nahin ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai aur iski sanad qawi nahin hai."
3519,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey haath ki ungliyon ya apney haath ki ungliyon par gin kar bataya ke « Subhanallah » nisf meezaan rahega aur « الحمد لله » us purey paldey ko bhar dega aur « الله أكبر » aasman o zamin key darmiyan ki sari jagahon ko bhar dega , roza aadha sabr hai, aur paki nisf eman hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai aur is hadees ko Shoba aur Sufiyan Sory ney Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat kya hai."
3520,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wuqoof Arfa key doran Arfa ki Sham aksar jo dua manga kartey they wo ye thi : اللهم لك الحمد كالذي نقول وخيرا مما نقول اللهم لك صلاتي ونسكي ومحياي ومماتي وإليك مآبي ولك رب تراثي اللهم إني أعوذ بك من عذاب القبر ووسوسة الصدر وشتات الأمر اللهم إني أعوذ بك من شر ما تجيء به الريح'' aey Allah ! terey liye hi hain sab taarifein jaisi ke tu ney hamen batai hain aur us sey behtar jaisi ke hum teri tareef kar saktey hain, aey Allah ! terey liye hi hai meri salaat , meri qurbani , meri zindagi aur meri maut , aur teri hi taraf hamen palat kar jana hai, aey merey rab ! terey liye hi hai meri meeras , aey Allah main azabe-qabr sey , seeney key waswasey sey aur mutafarriq o paraaganda kaam sey teri panah chahta hun aur aey Allah main teri panah chahta hun har us shar sey jisey hawa ley kar aati hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, iski sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai."
3521,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bahut sari duaeyn kin, magar mujhey un mein sey koi dua yad na rahi , mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! duaeyn to aap ney bahut si kin magar main koi dua yad na rakh saka , aap ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisi chiz na bata dun jo un sab chizon (duaaon) ki Jaamey ho, kaho : (اللهم إنا نسألك من خير ما سألك منه نبيك محمد صلى الله عليه وسلم ونعوذ بك من شر ما استعاذ منه نبيك محمد صلى الله عليه وسلم وأنت المستعان وعليك البلاغ wala حول wala قوة إلا بالله) ''aey Allah ! hum tujh sey wo bhalai (khair) maangtey hain jo tujh sey terey Nabi Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maangi hai aur hum teri panah chahtey hain us shar (burai) sey jis sey terey Nabi Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney panah maangi hai, tu hi madadgar hai, aur terey hi ikhtiyar mein hai (khair aur shar ka ( pahchaan'naa, aur gunah sey bachney ki taqat aur ibadat karney ki quwat Allah key saharey key baghair mumkin nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3522,"mainey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : Ummul-momenin ! jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka qiyam aap key yahan hota to aap ki ziyada tar dua kya hoti thi? unhoney kaha : aap ziyada tar : (يا مقلب القلوب ثبت قلبي على دينك) ''aey dilon key pherney waley ! merey dil ko apney Deen par jama dey.'' padhtey they, khud mainey bhi aap sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap aksar ye dua : (يا مقلب القلوب ثبت قلبي على دينك) kyon padhtey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''aey Umme-Salma ! koi bhi shakhs aisa nahin hai jis ka dil Allah ki ungliyon mein sey uski do ungliyon key darmiyan na ho, to Allah jisey chahta hai (deene-haq par) qaaim aur sabit qadam rakhta hai aur jisey chahta hai uska dil tedha kar deta hai phir (Raavi hadees) Muaz ney aayat : (ربنا لا تزغ قلوبنا بعد إذ هديتنا) ''aey hamarey parwardigar ! hamein hidayat dey deney key baad hamarey dilon mein kaji (gumrahi) na paida kar'' (Aale-Imran : 8) padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha, Nawaas bin Samaan , Anas , Jabir , Abdullah bin Amr aur Naeem bin Ammar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3523,"Khalid bin Waleed Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey shikayat kartey huye kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main raat bhar neend na aaney ki wajeh sey so nahin paata hun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum apney bistarey par soney key liye jaao to padho : (اللهم رب السموات السبع وما أظلت ورب الأرضين وما أقلت ورب الشياطين وما أضلت كن لي جارا من شر خلقك كلهم جميعا أن يفرط علي أحد منهم أو أن يبغي عز جارك وجل ثناؤك wala إله غيرك لا إله إلا أنت) ''aey Allah ! saton aasmano , aur jin par wo saya figan hain un sab key Rab ! sari zaminon aur un sari chizon key Rab jinka wo bojh uthaey huye hain aur aey shayatin aur jinhen unhoney gumrah kiya hai un sab key Rab ! apni sari makhluq key shar sey bachaney key liye mera padosi bin ja, taake un mein sey koi mujh par na zulm aur ziyadti kar sakey, aur na hi baghawat aur sarkashi ka murtakib (mujrim) ho, tera padosi ba-izzat ho, aur teri sanaa (aur tareef ( badh chadh kar ho, terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin mabood to bas tu hi hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin hai. 2- Hakam bin Zuher jo is hadees key eik Raavi hain, baaz muhaddeseen un ki bayan karda hadees nahin letey. 3- ye hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik dusri sanad sey mursal tareeqe sey aai hai."
3524,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko jab koi kaam sakht takleef aur pareshani mein dal deta to aap ye dua padhtey : (يا حي يا قيوم برحمتك أستغيث) ''aey zinda aur hamesha rehney waley ! teri rehmat key waseeley sey teri madad chahta hun.''
3525,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : « يا ذا الجلال والإكرام » ko lazim pakdo (yani : apni duaaon mein barabar padhtey raha karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, mehfooz nahin hai. 2- ye hadees Hammad bin Salma ney Humaid sey, unhoney Hasan Basri key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (mursalan) riwayat ki hai, aur ye ziyada sahih hai. aur Muammal sey is mein ghalati hui hai, chunanche unhoney « an Humaid an Anas » diya, jabkey is mein unka koi mutaabe nahin hai."
3526,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jo shakhs apney bistar par pak aur saaf ho kar soney key liye jaey aur Allah ka zikr kartey huye usey neend aa jaey to raat key jis kisi lamhey mein bhi bedaar ho kar wo duniya aur aakhirat ki jo koi bhi bhalai , Allah sey maangeyga Allah usey wo chiz zarur ata karega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Shehar bin Hoshab sey ba-tareeq : (أبي ظبية an عمرو بن عبسة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
3527,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko dua maangtey huye suna wo keh raha tha : (اللهم إني أسألك تمام النعمة) ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey nemat تامہ mang raha hun''  aap ney us shakhs sey puchha : ''nemat تامہ kya chiz hai?'' us shakhs ney kaha : mainey eik dua maangi hai aur mujhey ummid hai ke mujhey us sey khair hasil hogi , aap ney farmaya : ''beshak nemat تامہ mein jannat ka daakhila aur jahannam sey najat dono aatey hain.'' aap ney eik aur aadmi ko (bhi) dua maangtey huye suna, wo keh raha tha : ''« يا ذا الجلال والإكرام »''  aap ney farmaya : ''teri dua qubul hui to mang ley (jo tujhey maangna ho)'' ,aap ney eik shakhs ko suna wo keh raha tha, « اللهم إني أسألك الصبر » ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey sabr maangta hun'' ,aap ney farmaya : ''tu ney Allah sey bula maangi hai isliye to aafiyat bhi mang ley.''"
3528,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi neend mein dar jaey to (ye dua) padhey : (أعوذ بكلمات الله التامات من غضبه وعقابه وشر عباده ومن همزات الشياطين وأن يحضرون) ''main panah maangta hun Allah key kamil aur jaame kalimon key zariey Allah key ghazab , Allah key azab aur Allah key bandon key shar aur fasad aur shayatin key waswason sey aur is baat sey ke wo hamarey paas aayen.'' (ye dua padhney sey) ye pareshan kun khuwab usey kuchh nuqsan na pahuncha sakeyga. (taake wo usey yad kar lein, na ke taawez key taur par) Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma apney baligh bachon ko ye dua sikha detey they, aur jo bachchey nabaligh hotey they unkey liye ye dua kaghaz par likh kar unkey galey mein latka detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3529,"main Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma key paas aaya aur un sey kaha : aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey jo hadisein sun rakhi hain un mein sey koi hadees hamein sunaaiye, to unhoney eik likha huwa waraq hamarey aagey badha diya, aur kaha : ye wo kaghaz hai jisey Rasoolullah ney hamein likh kar diya hai, jab mainey usey dekha to is mein likha huwa tha ke abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi aisi dua bata dijiye jisey main subah aur Sham mein padha karun, aap ney farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! (ye dua) padha karo : (اللهم فاطر السموات والأرض عالم الغيب والشهادة لا إله إلا أنت رب كل شيء ومليكه أعوذ بك من شر نفسي ومن شر الشيطان وشركه وأن أقترف على نفسي سوءا أو أجره إلى مسلم) ''aey Allah ! aasmano aur zaminon key paida karney waley , khuli hui aur poshida chizon key janney waley , koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai siwaye terey , to har chiz ka Rab (paalney wala) aur uska badshah hai, aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun apney nafs key shar sey, shetan key shar aur uskey jaal aur phandon sey aur main teri panah chahta hun is baat sey ke main apney aap key khilaf koi gunah kar bethun, ya us gunah mein kisi musalman ko mulawwis kar dun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3530,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah sey badh kar koi ghairat mand nahin hai, isi liye Allah Taala ney behayai ki cheezen haram kar di hain chahey wo khuley taur par hon ya poshida taur par, aur koi bhi aisa nahin hai jisey Allah sey ziyada madah (tareef) pasand ho, isi liye Allah ney apni zaat ki tareef khud aap ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3531,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kiya : aap mujhey koi aisi dua bata dijiye jisey main apni namaz mein manga karun padhi. , aap ney farmaya : ''kaho : (اللهم إني zulmat نفسي ظلما كثيرا wala يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت فاغفر لي مغفرة من عندك وارحمني إنك أنت الغفور الرحيم) ''aey Allah ! mainey apney aap par bada zulm kiya hai, jabke gunahon ko terey siwa koi aur bakhsh nahin sakta, isliye to mujhey apni inayat khas sey bakhsh dey, aur mujh par reham farma, tu hi bakhshney wala aur reham farmanewala hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, aur ye Les bin Saad ki riwayat hai."
3532,"Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye, to un unhoney koi baat suni (jis ki unhoney aap ko khabar di) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par chadh gaey, aur puchha : ''main kon hun?'' logon ney kaha : aap Allah key Rasool ! aap par Allah ki salamti nazil ho, aap ney farmaya : ''main Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Abdul-Muttalib hun, Allah ney makhluq ko paida kiya to mujhey sab sey behtar giroh mein paida kiya, phir us giroh mein bhi do giroh bana diye aur mujhey un dono girohon mein sey behtar giroh mein rakha, phir un mein mukhtalif qabiley bana diye, to mujhey sab sey behtar qabiley mein rakha, phir unhen gharon mein baant diya to mujhey achchhey nasab waley behtareen khandan aur ghar mein paida kiya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3533,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik aisey darkht key paas sey guzrey jiski pattiyan sookh gaee thin, aap ney is par apni chhadi maari to pattiyan jhad padin, aap ney farmaya : ''« الحمد لله وسبحان الله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر » kehney sey bandey key gunah aisey hi jhad jatey hain jaisey us darkht ki pattiyan jhad gaeen.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Aamash ka Anas sey samaa (sun'na), hum nahin jantey, haan ye baat zarur hai ke unhoney Anas ko dekha hai."
3534,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney maghrib key baad das baar kaha : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو على كل شيء قدير) Allah uski subah tak hifazat key liye musalleh farishtey bhejeyga jo uski shetan sey hifazat karengey aur uskey liye unkey iwaz das nekiyan likhi jaeyngi jo usey ajr aur sawab ka mustahiq banaeyngi aur uski mohlik buraiyan aur gunah mita dengi aur usey das musalman ghulam azad karney ka sawab milega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai aur hum isey sirf Les bin Saad ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- aur hum Imaara ka Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey samaa (sun'na), nahin jantey."
3535,"main Safwan bin Assaal Muraadi (Raziallahu anhu) key paas mozon par masah ka masla poochhney aaya, unhoney (mujh sey) puchha aey Zar kon sa jazba tumhen ley kar yahan aaya hai, mainey kaha : ilm ki talash aur talab mujhey yahan ley kar aai hai, unhoney kaha : farishtey ilm ki talab aur talash sey khush ho kar Talibe ilm key liye apney par bichhate hain, mainey un sey kaha : peshab pakhaney sey faraaghat key baad mozon par masah ki baat merey dil mein khatki (ke masah karen ya na karen) main khud bhi Sahabiye Rasool hun, main aap sey ye poochhney aaya hun ke kya aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko is silsiley mein koi baat bayan kartey huye suna hai? kaha : ji haan (suni hai) jab hum safar par hotey ya safar karney waley hotey to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamein hukm detey they ke ''hum safar key doran teen din aur raat apney mozey na nikalen, magar ghusle-janabat key liye, pakhana peshab kar key aur so kar uthney par mozey na nikalen.''  (pehney rahen, masah ka waqt aaye un par masah kar lein) mainey un sey puchha : kya aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey insan ki khahish aur tamanna ka zikr kartey huye suna hai? unhoney kaha : haan, hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar kar rahey they, us doran ke hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas they eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney aap ko ya Muhammad ! keh kar buland aawaz sey pukara , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey usi ki aawaz mein jawab diya, ''aa jaao (main yahan hun)'' hamney us sey kaha : tumhara naas ho, apni aawaz dheemi kar lo, kyonkey tum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ho, aur tumhen is sey mana kiya gaya hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas buland aawaz sey bola jaey, Erabi (dehati) ney kaha : (na) qism Allah ki main apni aawaz past nahin karunga, usney « المرء يحب القوم ولما يلحق بهم  keh kar aap sey apni intehai mohabbat aur talluq ka izhar kiya. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : (المرء مع من أحب يوم القيامة) ''jo shakhs jis shakhs sey ziyada mohabbat karta hai qiyamat key din wo isi key sath rahega.'' wo hum sey (yani Zar kehtey hain hum sey Safwan bin Assaal) hadees bayan kartey rahey yahan tak ke unhoney pashchim samt (maghrib ki taraf) main eik aisey darwazey ka zikr kiya jiski chodai sattar saal ki masafat (doori) key barabar hai (Raavi ko shak ho gaya hai ye kaha ya ye kaha) ke darwazey ki chodai itni hogi. sawar is mein chaleyga to chaalis saal ya sattar saal main eik sirey sey doosrey sirey tak pahunchega, Sufiyan (Raavi) kehtey hain : ye darwaza Sham ki janib padeyga, jab Allah ney aasmano aur zamin ko paida kiya hai tabhi Allah ney ye darwaza bhi banaya hai aur ye darwaza tauba karney walon key liye khula huwa hai aur (tauba ka ye darwaza) us waqt tak band na hoga jab tak ke suraj us darwaze ki taraf sey (yani pashchim sey) tulu na honey lagey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3536,"main Safwan bin Assaal Muraadi (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya, unhoney puchha : tumhen kya chiz yahan ley kar aai hai? mainey kaha : ilm hasil karney aaya hun, unhoney kaha : mujhey ye hadees pahunchi hai ke ''farishtey Talibe ilm key kaam (aur maqsad) sey khush ho kar Talibe ilm key liye apney par bichha detey hain.''  wo kehtey hain : mainey kaha : merey ji mein ye khayal guzra ya merey dil mein mozon par maseh key barey mein kuch baat khatki, to kya us barey mein aap ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki koi baat yad hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan , hum jab safar mein hon (ya safar karney waley hon) to hamein hukm diya gaya ke ''hum teen din tak apney mozey pairon sey na nikalen, siwaye janabat ki surat mein, pakhana kar key aaye hon ya peshab kar key, ya so kar uthey hon to mozey na nikalen.'' phir mainey un sey puchha : kya aap ko mohabbat aur chaahat key silsiley mein bhi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki koi baat yad hai? unhoney kaha : haan, hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath kisi safar mein they to aap ko eik aadmi ney jo logon mein sab sey peechhey chal raha tha aur ganwaar, bewaquf aur sakht mizaj tha, buland aawaz sey pukara , kaha : ya Muhammad ! ya Muhammad ! logon ney us sey kaha : thehar , thehar , is tarah pukarney sey tumhen roka gaya hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey usi ki tarah bhari aur buland aawaz mein jawab diya : ''badh aa, badh aa, aa ja aa ja.'' (wo jab qarib aa gaya) to bola : aadmi kuchh logon sey mohabbat karta hai lekin unkey darjey tak nahin pahuncha hota hai, to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo insan jis sey mohabbat karta hai isi key sath uthaya jaeyga.'' Zar kehtey hain : wo mujh sey hadees bayan kartey rahey yahan tak ke unhoney mujh sey bayan kiya ke ''Allah ney maghrib mein tauba ka eik darwaza banaya hai jiski chodai sattar saal ki masafat (doori) hai, wo band na kiya jaeyga yahan tak ke suraj udhar sey nikalney lagey (yani qiyamat tak) aur isi silsiley mein Allah Taala ka ye qol hai : (يوم يأتي بعض آيات ربك لا ينفع نفسا إيمانها) ''jis din ke terey Rab ki baaz aayaat ka zuhoor hoga us waqt kisi shakhs ko uska eman kaam na dega'' Al-Anaam-158). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3537,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah apney bandey ki tauba us waqt tak qubul karta hai jab tak ke (maut key waqt) uskey galey sey khar khar ki aawaz na aaney lagey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3538,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala apney bandey ki tauba sey us sey kahin ziyada khush hota hai jitna ke koi shakhs apni khoi hui chiz (khaas taur sey gumshuda sawari ki oontni paa kar khush hota hai).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, yani abu-Zinad ki riwayat sey. 2- ye hadees Mak'hool sey bhi un ki apni sanad sey aai hai, unhoney Abu-Zar key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood, Noman bin Bashir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3539,"jab un ki maut ka waqt qarib aa gaya to unhoney kaha : mainey tum logon sey eik baat chhupa rakhi hai, (main usey is waqt zahir kar dena chahta hun) mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''agar tum log gunah na karo to Allah eik aisi makhluq paida kar dey jo gunah karti phir Allah unhen bakhshta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Muhammad bin Kaab sey aai hai aur unhoney isey abu-Ayyub key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
3540,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''Allah kehta hai : aey Adam key betey ! jab tak to mujh sey duaaeyn karta rahega aur mujh sey apni umeeden aur tawaqqoaat wabasta rakheyga main tujhey bakhshta rahunga, chahey terey gunah kisi bhi darjey par pahunchey huye hon, mujhey kisi baat ki parwah aur dar nahin hai, aey Adam key betey ! agar terey gunah aasman ko chhuney lagen phir to mujh sey maghfirat talab karney lagey to main tujhey bakhsh dunga aur mujhey kisi baat ki parwah na hogi. aey Adam key betey ! agar to zamin barabar bhi gunah kar bethey aur phir mujh sey (maghfirat talab karney key liye) miley lekin merey sath kisi tarah ka shirk na kiya ho to main terey paas uskey barabar maghfirat ley kar aaunga (aur tujhey bakhsh dunga).''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai aur hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3541,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney sau rahmatein paida kin aur eik rehmat apni makhluq key darmiyan duniya mein rakhi, jiski badolat wo duniya main eik doosrey key sath rehmat aur shafqat sey pesh aatey hain, jabke Allah key paas ninnanwey (99) rahmatein hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Salman aur Jundub bin Abdullah bin Sufiyan Bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3542,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar momin ko malum ho jaey ke Allah key yahan kaisi kaisi sazaaeyn hain to jannat ki koi ummid na rakhey, aur agar kafir ye jaan ley ke Allah ki rehmat kitni wasee aur azeem hai to jannat mein pahunchney sey koi bhi na-umeed aur mayus na ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abu Alaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo apney walid aur unkey walid Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain."
3543,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah ney makhluq ko paida kiya to usney apney aap sey apni zaat par likh diya (yani apney aap par farz kar liya) ke meri rehmat merey ghazab (ghusse) par ghalib rahegi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3544,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam masjid mein aaye , eik shakhs namaz padh raha tha aur dua maangtey huye wo apni dua mein keh raha tha : (اللهم لا إله إلا أنت المنان بديع السموات والأرض ذا الجلال والإكرام) ''aey Allah ! terey siwa koi aur mabood bar-haq nahin hai, tu hi ehsan karney wala hai tu hi aasmano aur zamin ka bananey aur paida karney wala hai, aey badai waley aur karam karney waley (meri dua qubul farma).''  Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho usney kis chiz sey dua ki hai? usney Allah sey uskey us Isme-Azam (bade naam) key zariye dua ki hai ke jab bhi uskey zariye dua ki jaeygi Allah usey qubul kar ley ga, aur jab bhi uskey zariye koi chiz maangi jaeygi usey ata farma dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Anas sey aai hai."
3545,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us shakhs ki naak khaak aalud ho jis key paas mera zikr kiya jaey aur wo shakhs mujh par durood na bhejey, aur us shakhs ki bhi naak khaak aalud ho jiski zindagi mein Ramzan ka mahina aaya aur uski maghfirat huye baghair wo mahina guzar gaya, aur us shakhs ki bhi naak khaak aalud ho jisney apney maa baap ko budhapey mein paya ho aur wo dono usey unkey sath husne-suluk na karney ki wajeh sey jannat ka mustahiq na bana sakey hon.''  Abdur-Rehman ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : mera khayal ye hai ke aap ney dono maa baap kaha. ya ye kaha ke un mein sey kisi eik ko bhi budhapey mein paya (aur un ki khidmat kar key apni maghfirat na kar li ho). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- Rabaee bin Ibrahim Ismail bin Ibrahim key bhai hain aur ye Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur ye ibne Aleh padhi. hain. 3- is bab mein Jabir aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, wo kehtey hain : jab majlis mein aadmi eik baar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko durood bhej dey to us majlis mein chahey jitni baar aap ka naam aaye eik baar durood bhej dena har baar key liye kafi hoga (yani har baar durood bhejna zaruri na hoga)."
3546,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bakheel (kanjoos) wo hai jis key samney mera zikr kiya jaey aur phir bhi wo mujh par salaat (durood) na bhejey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3547,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye dua kartey they : (اللهم برد قلبي بالثلج والبرد والماء البارد اللهم نق قلبي من الخطايا كما نقيت الثوب الأبيض من الدنس) ''aey Allah ! to merey dil ko thanda kar dey barf aur oley sey aur thandey pani sey aur merey dil ko khtaaon sey paak aur saaf kar dey jaisa ke tu ney safed kapdey ko mail kuchail sey paak aur saaf kiya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3548,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey jis kisi key liye dua ka darwaza khola gaya to uskey liye (goya) rehmat key darwazey khol diye gaey, aur Allah sey maangi janey wali chizon mein sey jisey wo dey us sey ziyada koi chiz pasand nahin ke us sey aafiyat maangi jaey.''"
3549,"Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Bakar sey riwayat ki hai aur Abdur-Rehman ney Musa bin Aqba sey , Musa ney Nafey sey , aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey , aap ney farmaya : ''Allah sey jo cheezen bhi maangi jati hain un mein Allah ko aafiyat sey ziyada mehbub koi chiz bhi nahin hai.''"
3550,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''hamari ummat ki umrein saath aur sattar (saal) key darmiyan hain aur thodey hi log aisey hongey jo us had ko paar karengey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai yani Muhammad bin Amr ki riwayat sey jisey wo abi Salma sey aur abu-Salma Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- hum (abu-Salma ki) is hadees ko sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 3- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai.
3551,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam dua maangtey huye ye kehtey they : (رب أعني wala تعن علي وانصرني wala تنصر علي وامكر لي wala تمكر علي واهدني ويسر الهدى لي وانصرني على من بغى علي رب اجعلني لك شكارا لك ذكارا لك رهابا لك مطواعا لك مخبتا إليك أواها منيبا رب تقبل توبتي واغسل حوبتي وأجب دعوتي وثبت حجتي وسدد لساني واهد قلبي واسلل سخيمة صدري) ''aey merey Rab ! meri madad kar , merey khilaf kisi ki madad na kar , aey Allah ! to meri taeed aur nusrat farma aur merey khilaf kisi ki taeed aur nusrat na farma, aur merey liye tadbeer farma aur merey khilaf kisi key liye tadbeer na farma, aur aey Allah ! to mujhey hidayat bakhsh aur hidayat ko merey liye aasan farma, aur aey Allah ! meri madad farma us shakhs key muqabil mein jo merey khilaf baghawat aur sarkashi kerey. aey merey Rab ! to mujhey apna bahut ziyada shukar-guzar banda bana ley, apna bahut ziyada yad aur zikr karney wala bana ley, apney sey bahut darney wala bana dey, apni bahut ziyada itaat karney wala bana dey, aur apney samney aajizi karney wala bana dey, aur apney sey dard aur bayan karney aur apni taraf ruju karney wala bana dey. aey merey Rab ! meri tauba qubul farma aur merey gunah dho dey, aur meri dua qubul farma , aur meri hujjat (meri daleel) ko sabit aur thos bana dey, aur meri zaban ko theek baat kehney wali bana dey, merey dil ko hidayat farma, aur merey seeney sey khot keena hasad nikal dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3552,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney apney ooper zulm karney waley key khilaf bad dua ki to usney us sey badla ley liya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey Hamza ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Hamza key barey mein baaz ehle-ilm ney unkey hafizey key talluq sey kalam kiya hai, aur ye Memun hain."
3553,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney das baar : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو على كل شيء قدير) ''Allah wahid key siwa koi mabood nahin hai, uska koi shareek aur saajhi nahin usi key liye hai mulk (badshahat) usi key liye hai sari tareefen, wohi zindagi bakhshta hai aur wohi maarta hai aur wo har chiz par qadir hai.''  kaha to ye (uska ajr) aulade Ismail mein sey chaar ghulam azad karney key barabar hoga.''  ye hadees abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey moqufan bhi riwayat hui hai."
3554,"mainey Safiya Raziallahu anhuma ko kehtey huye suna : merey paas Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif laye, us waqt merey samney khajoor ki chaar hazar guthliyon ki dher thi, main un guthliyon key zariye tasbih padha karti thi, mainey kaha : mainey in key zariye tasbih padhi hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kya ye achchha na hoga ke main tumhen is sey ziyada tasbih ka tariqa bata dun jitni tu ney padhi hain?'' mainey kaha : (zarur) mujhey bataiye, to aap ney farmaya : (سبحان الله عدد خلقه) ''main teri makhluqat ki tadaad key barabar teri tasbih bayan karti hun''  padh liya karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey Safiya ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain yani Haashim bin Saeed Koofi ki riwayat sey aur iski sanad maroof nahin hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai."
3555,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey paas sey guzrey aur wo (us waqt) apni masjid mein thin (jahan wo ba-qaeeda ghar mein namaz padhti thin), dophare mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka unkey paas sey phir guzar huwa, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey puchha : tab sey tum isi haal mein ho? (yani usi waqt sey is waqt tak tum zikr aur tasbih hi mein bethi ho) unhoney kaha : ji haan , aap ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen chand kalimey aisey na sikha dun jinhen tum keh liya karo. (aur phir pura sawab paao) wo kalimey ye hain : (سبحان الله عدد خلقه ، سبحان الله عدد خلقه ، سبحان الله عدد خلقه ، سبحان الله رضا نفسه ، سبحان الله رضا نفسه ، سبحان الله رضا نفسه ، سبحان الله زنة عرشه ، سبحان الله زنة عرشه ، سبحان الله زنة عرشه ، سبحان الله مداد كلماته ، سبحان الله مداد كلماته ، سبحان الله مداد كلماته). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman Aale-Talha key azad karda ghulam hain, wo Madina key rehney waley Shaikh hain aur Suqa (bharosemand) hain, ye hadees Masoodi aur Sory ney bhi un sey riwayat ki hai."
3556,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah (حيي كريم) hai yani zinda aur mojud hai aur shareef hai usey is baat sey sharam aati hai ke jab koi aadmi uskey samney haath phela dey to wo uskey dono haathon ko khaali aur nakam aur na-murad wapis kar dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, baaz dusron ney bhi ye hadees riwayat ki hai, lekin unhoney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai."
3557,eik shakhs apni do ungliyon key isharay sey dua karta tha to aap ney us sey kaha : ''eik sey eik sey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- yehi is hadees ka mafhoom ye hai ke aadmi tashahud mein ungliyon sey ishara kartey waqt sirf eik ungli sey ishara karey.
3558,"Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) member par chadhey, aur roey , phir kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hijrat key pehley saal member par chadhey , roey , phir kaha : Allah sey (gunahon sey) maafi aur musibaton aur gumrahiyon sey aafiyat talab karo kyonkey eman aur yaqin key baad kisi bandey ko aafiyat sey behtar koi chiz nahin di gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey yani abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3559,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs gunah kar key tauba kar ley aur apney gunah par naadim ho to wo chahey din bhar mein sattar baar bhi gunah kar daley wo gunah par Misr aur bazid nahin maana jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abu Nusaira ki riwayat sey jantey hain. aur iski sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai.
3560,"umr bin Khattab ney naya kapda pehnaa phir ye dua padhi :« الحمد لله الذي كساني ما أواري به عورتي وأتجمل به في حياتي » ''tamam tareefen us Allah key liye hain jisney mujhey aisa kapda pehnaya jis sey main apni sattar poshi karta hun aur apni zindagi mein husn aur jamaal paida karta hun.''  phir unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey huye suna : ''jisney naya kapda pehnaa phir ye dua padhi :« الحمد لله الذي كساني ما أواري به عورتي وأتجمل به في حياتي » phir usney apna puraanaa (utaara huwa) kapda liya aur usey sadqe mein dey diya, to wo Allah ki hifazat aur panah mein rahega zindagi mein bhi aur marney key baad bhi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3561,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Najad ki taraf eik fauj bheji to usney bahut sari ghanimat hasil kiya aur jald hi lot aai, (jang mein) na janey walon mein sey eik ney kaha : mainey is fauj sey behtar koi fauj nahin dekhi jo is fauj sey ziyada jald lot aaney wali aur ziyada maale ghanimat ley kar aaney wali ho. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya main tum logon ko eik aisey logon ki eik jamaat na bataaun jo ziyada ghanimat wali aur jald wapis aa janey wali ho? ye wo log hain jo namaze Fajr mein hazir hotey hain phir beth kar Allah ka zikr kartey hain yahan tak ke suraj nikal aata hai ye log (un sey) jald lot aaney waley aur (un sey) ziyada maale ghanimat laney waley hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Hammad bin abi Humaid ye Muhammad bin Abi Humaid hain, aur ye Abu Ibrahim Ansari Madni hain. hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain."
3562,"unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Umra karney ki ijazat maangi to aap ney (ijazat detey huye) kaha : ''aey merey bhai ! apni dua mein hamein bhi shareek rakhna, bhoolna nahin.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3563,"eik makatib ghulam (wo ghulam jisne apni azaadi ke liye koi muhaaida kar rakha ho) ney padhi. unkey paas aa kar kaha ke main apni makatibat ki raqam ada nahin kar paa raha hun, aap hamari kuchh madad farma dijiye to unhoney kaha : kya main tum ko kuchh aisey kalimey na sikha dun jinhen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein sikhaey they? agar terey paas (seer) pahad key barabar bhi qarz ho to teri janib sey Allah usey ada farma dega, unhoney kaha : kaho : (اللهم اكفني بحلالك an حرامك وأغنني بفضلك عمن سواك) ''aey Allah ! to hamein halal dey kar haram sey kifaayat kar dey, aur apney Fazal (rizq, maal aur dolat) sey nawaz kar apney siwa kisi aur sey maangney sey be-niyaz kar dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3564,"mujhey shikayat hui (bimari hui), Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas tashrif laye, us waqt main dua kar raha tha : (اللهم إن كان أجلي قد حضر فأرحني وإن كان متأخرا فارفغني وإن كان بلاء فصبرني) ''aey merey Rab ! agar meri maut ka waqt aa pahuncha hai to mujhey (maut dey kar) rahat dey aur aur agar meri maut baad mein ho to mujhey utha kar khada kar dey (yani sehat dedey) aur agar ye aazmaaish hai to mujhey sabr dey.''  Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : ''kaisey kaha'' to unhoney jo kaha tha usey dohraayaa, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen apney pair sey thokaa diya phir aap ney farmaya : (اللهم عافه أو اشفه) ''aey Allah ! inhen aafiyat dey, ya shifaa dey.''  iskey baad mujhey apni takleef ki phir kabhi shikayat nahin hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3565,"jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi bimar ki iyaadat kartey to ye dua padhtey they : (اللهم أذهب البأس رب الناس واشف فأنت الشافي لا شفاء إلا شفاؤك شفاء لا يغادر سقما) ''aey Allah ! aey logon key Rab ! azab aur takleef ko door kar dey aur shifaa dedey, tu hi shifaa deney wala hai, teri di hui shifaa key siwa koi shifaa nahin hai, aisi shifaa dey ke bimari kuchh bhi baqi na rahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3566,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni (namaz) witr mein ye dua padhtey they : (اللهم إني أعوذ برضاك من سخطك وأعوذ بمعافاتك من عقوبتك وأعوذ بك منك لا أحصي ثناء عليك أنت كما أثنيت على نفسك). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Ali ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, yani Hammad ibne Salma ki riwayat sey. faeyda padhi. : ''aey Allah ! main teri narazagi sey bach kar teri raza aur khushnoodi ki panah mein aata hun, aey Allah ! main terey azab aur saza sey bach kar terey azab aur saza se bachkar teri maafi ki panah chahta hun, aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun terey ghazab sey , main teri sanaa (tareef) ka ihaata aur shumar nahin kar sakta to to wesa hi hai jaisa ke tu ney khud apney aap ki sanaa aur tareef ki hai.''"
3567,"Saad bin abi Waqas apney beton ko ye kalimey aisey hi sikhatey they jaise ke chhotey bachchon ko likhna padhna sikhaaney wala muallim sikhata hai aur kehtey they ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam in kalimaat key zariey har namaz key akheer mein Allah ki panah maangtey they. (wo kalimey ye they) : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الجبن وأعوذ بك من البخل وأعوذ بك من أرذل العمر وأعوذ بك من فتنة الدنيا وعذاب القبر) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah leta hun buzdili sey, aey Allah ! main teri panah leta hun kanjusi sey, aey Allah ! main teri panah leta hun zaleel tareen umr sey (yani us budhapey sey jis mein aql aur hawas kuchh na reh jaey) aur panah maangta hun duniya key fitne aur qabr key azab sey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi kehtey hain : Abu-Is'haq Hamdaani is hadees mein iztirab ka shikar they, kabhi kehtey they : riwayat hai Amr bin Memun sey aur wo riwayat kartey hain umr sey, aur kabhi kisi aur sey kehtey aur us riwayat mein iztirab kartey they."
3568,"wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik aurat key paas gaey, uskey aagey khajoor ki guthliyaan thin ya kankariyaan, unkey zariey wo tasbih padha karti thi, aap ney us sey farmaya : ''kya main tumhen is sey aasan tariqa na bata dun? ya is sey afzal aur behtar tariqa na bata dun? (ke sawab mein bhi ziyada rahey aur lambi chodi ginti karney sey bhi bacha rahey) wo ye hai : (سبحان الله عدد ما خلق في السماء ، وسبحان الله عدد ما خلق في الأرض ، وسبحان الله عدد ما بين ذلك ، وسبحان الله عدد ما هو خالق ، والله أكبر مثل ذلك ، والحمد لله مثل ذلك ، wala حول wala قوة إلا بالله مثل ذلك) ''paaki hai Allah ki itni jitni usney aasman mein cheezen paida ki hain, aur paaki hai Allah ki itni jitni usney zamin mein cheezen paida ki hain, aur paaki hai uski itni jitni ke un dono key darmiyan cheezen hain, aur paaki hai uski itni jitni ke wo (aainda) paida karney wala hai, aur aisey hi Allah ki badai hai aur aisey hi Allah key liye hamd hai aur aisey hi لا حول wala قوۃ hai, (yani Allah ki makhluq ki tadaad key barabar).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Saad ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3569,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi subah aisi nahin hai ke Allah key bandey subah kartey hon aur us subah mein koi pukar kar kehney wala ye na kehta ho ke (سبحان الملك القدوس) ki tasbih padha karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
3570,"us doran ke hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas they ke usi doran Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aa kar arz kya : merey maa baap aap par qurban , ye Quran to merey seeney sey nikalta ja raha hai, mein usey mehfooz nahin rakh paa raha hun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' abul-Hasan ! kya main tumhen aisey kalmey na sikha dun ke jinkey zariey Allah tumhen bhi faeyda dey aur unhen bhi faeyda pahunchey jinhen tum ye kalmey sikhao ? aur jo tum seekho wo tumharey seeney mein mehfooz rahey '' , unhoney kaha : ji haan , aey Allah key Rasool ! aap hamen zarur sikhaaiye , aap ney farmaya : '' jab Juma ki raat ho aur raat key aakhiri tihai hissey main tum khadey ho saktey ho to uth kar us waqt ibadat karo kyonkey raat key teesrey pahar ka waqt aisa waqt hota hai jis mein farishtey bhi mojud hotey hain, aur dua us waqt maqbool hoti hai, merey bhai Yaqub (Alaihissalam) ney bhi apney beton sey kaha tha : « سوف أستغفر لكم ربي » yani main tumharey liye apney rab sey maghfirat talab karunga , aaney wali Juma ki raat mein , agar na uth sako to darmiyan pahar mein uth jaao , aur agar darmiyani hissey ( pahar ( mein na uth sako to pehley pahar hi mein uth jaao aur chaar rakat namaz padho , pehli rakat mein Sura Fatiha aur Sura Yasin padho, dusri rakat mein Sura Fatiha aur Ha-Mim Dukhan aur teesri rakat mein Sura Fatiha aur Sura Sajda aur chauthii rakat mein Sura Fatiha aur Mulk( mufassal ( padho , phir jab tashahud sey farigh ho jaao to Allah ki hamd bayan karo aur achey dhang sey Allah ki sanaa bayan karo, aur mujh par salaat ( durood ( bhejo , aur achey dhang sey bhejo aur sarey nabiyon salaat par) durood ( bhejo aur momin mardon aur momina aurton key liye maghfirat talab karo, aur un momin bhaiyon key liye bhi maghfirat ki dua karo, jo tum sey pehley us duniya sey ja chukey hain, phir ye sab kar chikney key baad ye dua padho : اللهم ارحمني بترك المعاصي أبدا ما أبقيتني وارحمني أن أتكلف ما لا يعنيني وارزقني حسن النظر فيما يرضيك عني اللهم بديع السموات والأرض ذا الجلال والإكرام والعزة التي لا ترام أسألك يا ألله يا رحمن بجلالك ونور وجهك أن تلزم قلبي حفظ كتابك كما علمتني وارزقني أن أتلوه على النحو الذي يرضيك عني اللهم بديع السموات والأرض ذا الجلال والإكرام والعزة التي لا ترام أسألك يا ألله يا رحمن بجلالك ونور وجهك أن تنور بكتابك بصري وأن تطلق به لساني وأن تفرج به an قلبي وأن تشرح به صدري وأن تغسل به بدني فإنه لا يعينني على الحق غيرك wala يؤتيه إلا أنت wala حول wala قوة إلا بالله العلي العظيم'' aey Allah ! mujh par reham farma is tarah ke jab tak to mujhey zinda rakh main hamesha gunah chhodey rakhun , aey Allah ! to mujh par reham farma is tarah ke main la yani chizon mein na padoon , jo cheezen teri raza o khushnudi ki hain unhen pehchanney key liye mujhey husney-nazar ( achi nazar ( dey , aey Allah ! aasmano aur zaminon key paida karney waley , Zul-Jalal (rob-dab waley) ikram ( izzat o buzurgi waley ( aisi izzat o martabat waley ke jis izzat ko hasil karney o paney ka koi qasd (irada) o irada hi na kar sakey, aey Allah ! aey badi rehmat waley mein terey jalal aur terey taabnak o munawwar chehrey key wasiley sey tujh sey maangta hun ke to merey dil ko apni kitab ( Quran pak ( key hifz key sath jod dey , jaisey tu ney mujhey Quran sikhaya hai wesay hi mein usey yad o mehfooz rakh sakun , aur to mujhey is baat ki tofiq dey ke main is kitab ko usi tareeqey aur usi dhang sey padhun jo tujhey mujh sey razi o khush kar dey , aey Allah ! aasmano aur zamin key paida karney waley , ( jaah ( o jalal aur buzurgi waley aur aisi izzat waley jis izzat ka koi irada ( tamanna aur khahish ( hi na kar sakey , aey Allah ! aey Rehman terey jalal aur terey chehrey key Noor key wasiley sey tujh sey maangta hun ke to apni kitab key zariey meri nigah ko munawwar kar dey ( mujhey kitabe-Ilahi ki Maarifat hasil ho jaey, aur meri zaban bhi usi key mutabiq chaley , aur usi key zariey merey dil ka gham door kar dey , aur uskey zariey mera Sina khol dey (main har achi o bhali baat ko samajhney lagun) aur uskey zariey merey badan ko dho dey (main pak o saaf rehney lagun ( kyonkey merey haq par chalney key liye terey siwa koi aur meri madad nahin kar sakta , aur na hi koi terey siwa mujhey haq dey sakta hai aur Allah jo bartar aur azeem hai uskey siwa buraiyon sey palatney aur nekiyon ko anjam deney ki tofiq kisi aur sey nahin mil sakti ''. aey abul-Hasan ! aisa hi karo, teen Juma , paanch Juma ya saat Juma tak , Allah key hukm sey dua qubul kar li jaeygi, aur qism hai us zaat ki jisney mujhey haq key sath bheja hai, us ko padh kar koi momin kabhi mehroom na rahega , Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : qism Allah ki ! Ali (Raziallahu anhu) paanch ya saat Juma thehrey hongey ke wo phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat main eik aisi hi majlis mein hazir huye aur aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! main is sey pehley chaar aayaten ya un jaisi do eik aayaten kam o besh yad kar paata tha, aur jab unhen dil mein aap hi aap dohrata tha to wo bhool jati thin, aur ab ye haal hai ke main chaalis aayaten seekhta hun ya chaalis sey do chaar kam ya zyada, phir jab main unhen apney aap dohrata hun to mujhey aisa lagta hai jaisey kitabullah meri aakhon key samney khuli hui rakhi hai) aur main rawani sey padhta chala jata hun (aur aisey hi mein is sey pehley hadees suna karta tha, phir jab main usey dohrata to wo dimagh sey nikal jati thi, lekin aaj mera haal ye hai ke main hadisein sunta hun phir jab main unhen bayan karta hun to un mein sey eik harf bhi kam nahin karta , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us moqey par irshad farmaya : ''qasam hai rabey-kaaba ki ! aey abul-Hasan tum momin ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Waleed bin Muslim ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3571,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah sey uska Fazal maango kyonkey Allah ko ye pasand hai ke us sey manga jaey, aur afzal ibadat ye hai) ke us dua key asar sey) kushadgi (aur khushhaali) ka intizar kya jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hammad bin Waqid ney aisi hi riwayat ki hai, aur unki riwayat mein ikhtilaf kya gaya hai, 2- Hammad bin Waqid ye Saffaar hain, Hafiz nahin hain, aur ye hamarey nazdik eik Basra Shekh hain, 3- Abu-Nueym ney ye hadees Israel sey , Israel ney Hakim bin Juber sey aur Hakim bin Juber ney eik shakhs key wastey sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, aur Abu-Nueym ki hadees sehat sey qarib tar hai."
3572,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye dua padhtey they : اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الكسل والعجز والبخل ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun, susti aur kahili sey, aajizi aur darmandgi sey aur kanjusi o bakheeli sey '' , aur isi sanad sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi aai hai ke aap panah maangtey they budhapey aur azabe-qabr sey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3573,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' zamin par koi bhi musalman aisa nahin hai jo gunah aur qata Rehmi ki dua ko chhod kar koi bhi dua karta ho aur Allah usey wo chiz na deta ho, ya uskey badley uskey barabar ki uski koi burai (koi musibat) door na kar deta ho'', is par eik shakhs ney kaha : tab to hum khub ( bahut ( duayen manga kerengey, aap ney farmaya : '' Allah us sey bhi ziyada deney wala hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3574,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum apney bistar par soney key liye jaao to jis tarah namaz key liye wuzu kartey ho wesa hi wuzu kar key jaao , phir dahiney karwat leto , phir ( ye ( dua padho : اللهم أسلمت وجهي إليك وفوضت أمري إليك وألجأت ظهري إليك رغبة ورهبة إليك لا ملجأ wala منجا منك إلا إليك آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت ونبيك الذي أرسلت ''aey Allah ! main tera tabey farman banda bin kar teri taraf mutawajjeh huwa , apna sab kuch tujhey saunp diya, tujh sey dartey huye aur raghbat kartey huye mainey tera sahara liya , na to meri koi ummid gaah hai aur na hi koi jaey najat , main teri is kitab par eman laya jo tu ney utaari hai aur terey us Nabi par eman laya jisey tu ney bheja hai'' , pas agar to apni us raat mein mar gaya to fitrat ( Islam ( par marega, Bara (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey dua key un alfaz ko dohraya taake yad ho jaeyn to dohraatey waqt mainey kaha : « آمنت برسولك الذي أرسلت » keh liya to aap ney farmaya : '' ( Rasool na kaho balke ( « آمنت بنبيك الذي أرسلت » kaho , main eman laya terey us Nabi par jisey tu ney bheja hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Bara bin Aazib sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai magar us raat key siwa kisi bhi riwayat mein hum ye nahin paatey ke wuzu ka zikr kya gaya ho."
3575,"hum eik barish wali sakht taareek raat mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko talash karney nikley taake aap hamen namaz padha den , chunanche main aapko paa gaya, aap ney farmaya : ''kaho ( padho ( '' , to mainey kuch na kaha : '' kaho '' aap ney phir farmaya , magar mainey kuch na kaha , ( kyonkey malum nahin tha kya kahun ? (aap ney phir farmaya : '' kaho '' , mainey kaha : kya kahun ? aap ney farmaya : « قل هو الله أحد » aur « Muawwizatein » ( « قل أعوذ برب الفلق » , padhi. « قل أعوذ برب الناس » ( subh o Sham teen martaba padh liya karo, ye ( suraten ( tumhen har shar sey bachaeyn gi aur mehfooz rakhengi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- abu-Saeed Baraad : ye Usaid bin abi Usaid madni hain."
3576,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey baap key paas aaye , hamney aap key khaney key liye kuch pesh kya to aap ney is mein sey khaya , phir aap key liye kuch khajuren laee gaeen , to aap khajuren khaney aur guthli apni dono ungliyon shahadat aur bech ki ungli sey) dono ko mila kar) phainktey jatey they, Shoba kehtey hain : jo main keh raha hun wo mera guman o khayal hai, Allah ney chaha to sahih hoga, aap dono ungliyon key bich mein guthli rakh kar phenk detey they, phir aap key samney peeney ki koi chiz laee gaee to aap ney pi aur apney daain janib haath waley ko thamaa diya ( jab aap chalney lagey to) aap ki sawari ki lagaam thaamey thaamey merey baap ney aap sey arz kya, aap hamarey liye dua farma dijiye , aap ney farmaya : « اللهم بارك لهم فيما رزقتهم واغفر لهم وارحمهم » '' aey Allah ! unkey rizq mein barkat ata farma aur unhen bakhsh dey aur un par rehmat nazil farma ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi ye hadees Abdullah bin basar sey aai hai."
3577,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' jo shakhs kahey : « أستغفر الله العظيم الذي la إله إلا هو الحي القيوم وأتوب إليه » ''main maghfirat maangta hun us buzurg o bartar Allah sey jis key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai, jo zinda hai aur har chiz ka nigehban hai aur main usi ki taraf ruju karta hun '' , to uski maghfirat kar di jaeygi agar-che wo lashkar ( o fauj ( sey bhag hi kyon na aaya ho . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3578,"eik na-bina shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur kaha : aap dua farma dijiye ki Allah mujhey aafiyat dey , aap ney farmaya : '' agar tum chaho to main dua karun aur agar chaho to sabr kiye raho , kyonkey ye tumharey liye ziyada behtar ( o sood mand ( hai ''. usney kaha : dua hi kar dijiye , to aap ney isey hukm diya ke '' wo wuzu karey , aur achi tarah sey wuzu karey aur ye dua padh kar dua karey :  (اللهم إني أسألك وأتوجه إليك بنبيك محمد نبي الرحمة إني توجهت بك إلى ربي في حاجتي هذه لتقضى لي اللهم فشفعه) '' aey Allah ! main tujh sey maangta hun aur terey Nabi Muhammad jo Nabi rehmat hain key waseeley sey teri taraf mutawajjeh hota hun, mainey aap key wastey sey apni is zarurat mein apney rab ki taraf tawajjoh ki hai taake to aey Allah ! meri ye zarurat puri kar dey to aey Allah to merey barey mein unki shafaat qubul kar padhi. ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai aur hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain yani abu Jaafar ki riwayat sey , 2- aur Abu-Jafar khutmi hain 3- aur Usman bin Hanif ye Sehal bin Hanif key bhai hain."
3579,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' rab taala apney bandey sey sab sey ziyada qarib raat key aakhiri nisf hissey key darmiyan mein hota hai, to agar tum un logon mein sey ho sako jo raat key us hissey mein Allah ka zikr kartey hain to tum bhi us zikr mein shamil hokar un logon mein sey ho jaao (yani tahajjud padho) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3580,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai ke mera banda kamil banda wo hai jo mujhey us waqt yad karta hai jab wo jang key waqt apney madde-muqaabil ( dushman ( key samney khada ho raha hota hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, iski sanad qawi nahin hai, us eik hadees key siwa hum Imaara bin Zaakara ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi aur riwayat nahin jantey, 2- Allah key qol « وهو ملاق قرنه » ka maana o matlab ye hai ke ladaai o jang key waqt, yani aisey waqt aur aisi ghadi mein bhi wo Allah ka zikr karta hai."
3581,"unkey baap ( Saad bin Ubada ( ney unhen Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat karney key liye aap key hawaley kar diya, wo kehtey hain : main namaz padh kar betha hi tha ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas sey guzrey , aap ney apney pair sey) mujhey apni taraf mutawajjeh karney key liye (eik thokar lagai phir farmaya : '' kya main tumhen jannat key darwazon mein sey eik darwaza na bata dun '' , mainey kaha : kyon nahin zarur bataiye , aap ney farmaya : '' wo (لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3582,koi bhi farishta (لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله) kahey baghair zamin sey nahin uthta ( nahin udtaa ( .
3583,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum sey farmaya : '' tumharey liye lazim aur zaruri hai ke tasbih padha karo tahleel aur taqdees kya karo padhi. aur ungliyon par) tasbeehaat waghera ko) guna karo, kyonkey un sey) qiyamat mein) puchha jaeyga aur unhen goyai ata kar di jaeygi, aur tum log ghaflat na baratna ke) Allah ki) rehmat ko bhool betho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey : hum is hadees ko sirf Haani bin Usman ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Muhammad bin Rabeea ney bhi Haani bin Usman sey riwayat ki hai."
3584,"jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jihad kartey ( ladtey ( to ye dua padhtey : « اللهم أنت عضدي وأنت نصيري وبك أقاتل » '' aey Allah ! to mera bazu hai, tu hi mera madadgar hai aur terey hi saharey mein ladtaa hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai 2- aur « عضدی » key maana hain to mera madadgar hai."
3585,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtar dua Arfa waley din ki dua hai aur mainey ab tak jo kuch ( bator zikr ( kaha hai aur mujh sey pehley jo doosrey nabiyon ney kaha hai un mein sab sey behtar dua ye hai : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير) '' Allah wahid key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai uska koi shareek nahin, usi key liye (sari kaeynat ki) badshahat hai, usi key liye sari tareefen hain aur wo har chiz par qadir hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- Hammad bin abi Humed ye Muhammad bin abi Humed hain aur un ki kunniyat Abu-Ibrahim Ansari madni hai aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik ziyada qawi nahin hain."
3586,"hamen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sikhaya , aap ney farmaya : '' kaho (اللهم اجعل سريرتي خيرا من علانيتي واجعل علانيتي صالحة اللهم إني أسألك من صالح ما تؤتي الناس من المال والأهل والولد غير الضال wala المضل) '' aey Allah ! mera baatin merey zahir sey achcha kar dey aur merey zahir ko nek kar dey . aur logon ko jo maal to biwi aur bachey ki shakal mein deta hai un mein sey achcha maal dey jo na khud gumrah hon aur na dusron ko gumrah karen ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain aur iski sanad qawi nahin hai."
3587,"mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaya, aap namaz padha rahey they, aap ney apna baayan haath apni baain raan par rakha tha, aur apna daayan haath apni daain raan par rakha , ungliyan band ki thin ( yani mutthi baandh rakhi thi (aur « سبابہ » ( shahadat ki ungli ( khol rakhi thi aur aap ye dua kar rahey they : (يا مقلب القلوب ثبت قلبي على دينك) '' aey dilon key pherney waley mera dil apney Deen par jama dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai."
3588,"jab tumhen dard ho to jahan dard aur takleef ho wahan haath rakho phir padho : (بسم الله أعوذ بعزة الله وقدرته من شر ما أجد من وجعي هذا) '' Allah key naam sey Allah ki izzat o qudrat key saharey main apni us takleef key shar sey jo main mehsus kar raha hun panah chahta hun ''. , phir ( dard ki jagah sey) haath hata lo phir aisey hi taaq ( teen ya paanch ya saat ( baar karo, kyonkey Anas bin Malik ney mujh sey bayan kya hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey aisa hi bayan kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, aur Muhammad bin Salim ye Basra Shekh hain."
3589,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey ye dua sikhai : (اللهم هذا استقبال ليلك واستدبار نهارك وأصوات دعاتك وحضور صلواتك أسألك أن تغفر لي) '' aey Allah ! ye teri raat key aaney aur terey din key janey ka waqt hai aur tujhey yad karney ki aawaazon aur teri namaz key liye pahunchney ka waqt hai main ( aisey waqt mein) apni maghfirat key liye tujh sey darkhaast karta hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai aur hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Hafsa bint abi Kasir ko hum nahin jantey aur na hi hum unkey baap ko jantey hain."
3590,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab bhi koi banda khuluse dil sey « لا إله إلا الله » kaheyga aur bade gunahon sey bachta rahega to uskey liye aasman key darwazey khol diye jaeyngey, aur ye kalma « لا إله إلا الله » arsh tak ja pahunchega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3591,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye dua padhtey they : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من منكرات الأخلاق والأعمال والأهواء) ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey buri aadaton, burey kamon aur buri khuwahishon sey panah maangta hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. aur Ziyad bin Ilaaqa key chacha ka naam Qutaba bin Malik hai aur ye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba mein sey hain."
3592,"eik baar hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padh rahey they padhi. , usi doran eik shakhs ney kaha : « الله أكبر كبيرا والحمد لله كثيرا وسبحان الله بكرة وأصيلا » ''Allah bahut badai wala hai, aur sari tareefen Allah hi key liye hain, aur paaki hai Allah Taala key liye subah aur shaam.''  Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (suna to) puchha : ''aisa aisa kis ney kaha hai?'' logon mein sey eik shakhs ney kaha : mainey kaha hai, aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''main is kalimey ko sun kar herat mein pad gaya, is kalimey key liye aasman key darwazey kholey gaey.'' ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : jab sey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye baat suni hai mainey in ka padhna kabhi nahin chhoda hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Hujjaaj bin Abi Usman ye Hujjaaj bin Maisraa Sawaaf hain, un ki kunniyat Abu-Salt hai aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa (bharosemand) hain. faeyda padhi. : ''namaz padh rahey they'' sey murad : hum log namaz shuru kar chukey they, itney mein wo aadmi aaya aur dua sanaa ki jagah usney yehi kalimaat kahey, is par Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uski taqreer (tasdeeq) kar di, to goya sanaa ki deegar duaaon key sath ye dua bhi eik sanaa hai, Imam Nasaai dua sanaa key baab hi mein is hadees ko latey hain, isliye baaz ulama ka ye kehna ke « سبحانک اللہم … » key siwaa sanaa ki baabat manqul sari duaaeyn sunan aur nawaafil sey talluq rakhti hain, sahih nahin hai."
3593,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un ki iyaadat ki (yahan Raavi ko shubha ho gaya) ya unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki iyaadat ki, to unhoney arz kiya : merey maa baap aap par qurban , aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa kaliam Allah ko ziyada pasand hai? aap ney farmaya : ''wo kaliam jo Allah ney apney farishton key liye muntakhab farmaya hai (aur wo ye hai) (سبحان ربي وبحمده سبحان ربي وبحمده) ''mera Rab paak hai aur tareef hai usi key liye , mera Rab paak hai aur har tarah ki hamd usi key liye zebaa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3594,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''azaan aur iqaamat key darmiyan maangi janey wali dua lotaai nahin jati.''  (yani qubul ho jati hai) logon ney puchha is doran hum kon si dua maangen , aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''duniya aur aakhirat (dono) mein aafiyat maango.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, Yahya bin Aban ney is hadees mein is ibarat ka izafa kiya hai ke un logon ney arz kiya ke hum kya kahen? aap ney farmaya : ''duniya aur aakhirat mein aafiyat (yani aman aur sukoon) maango.''"
3595,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''azaan aur iqaamat key darmiyan ki dua radd nahin ki jati hai'' (yani zarur qubul hoti hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu-Is'haq Hamdaani ney Bareed bin abi Maryam Koofi sey aur Bareed Koofi ney Anas key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aisey hi riwayat ki hai, aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
3596,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''halkey phulkey log aagey nikal gaey.''  logon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! ye halkey phulkey log kon hain? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ki yad aur zikr mein doobey rehney waley log, zikr unka bojh unkey ooper sey utaar kar rakh dega aur qiyamat key din halkey phulkey ayengey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3597,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : sari kaaenat sey ke jis par suraj tulu hota hai mujhey ye ziyada pasand hai ke main : (سبحان الله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر) ''Allah paak hai, tareef Allah key liye hai aur Allah key ilawa aur koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur Allah hi sab sey bada hai''  kahun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3598,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen log hain jinki dua radd nahin hoti : eik roze daar , jab tak ke roza na khol ley , ( doosrey ( aadil Imam, ( teesrey ( mazloom , uski dua Allah badliyon sey ooper tak pahunchata hai, uskey liye aasman key darwazey khol diye jatey hain, aur Rab kehta hai : meri izzat (qudrat) ki qism ! main teri madad karunga , bhaley kuchh muddat key baad hi kyon na ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Sa'daan قمی ye Sa'daan bin Bishr hain, in sey Esa bin Yunus , abu-Aasim aur kaee badey muhaddeseen ney riwayat ki hai. aur Au Mujahid sey murad Saad Taai hain. 4- aur Abu Mudilla Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key azad karda ghulam hain hum unhen sirf isi hadees key zariey sey jantey hain aur yehi hadees un sey is hadees sey ziyada mukammal aur lambi riwayat ki gaee hai."
3599,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye dua padhi : (اللهم انفعني بما علمتني وعلمني ما ينفعني وزدني علما الحمد لله على كل حال وأعوذ بالله من حال أهل النار) ''aey Allah ! mujhey us ilm sey nafa dey jo tu ney mujhey sikhaya hai aur mujhey wo ilm sikha jo mujhey faeyda dey aur mera ilm ziyada kar , har haal mein Allah hi key liye tareef hai aur main jahannamiyon key haal sey Allah ki panah maangta hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3600,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''logon key namaae aamal likhney waley farishton key ilawa bhi kuchh farishtey hain jo zamin mein ghoomtey phirtey rehtey hain, jab wo kisi qom ko Allah ka zikr kartey huye paatey hain to eik doosrey ko pukartey hain : aao aao yahan hai tumharey matlab aur maqsad ki baat , to wo log aa jatey hain, aur unhen qaribi aasman tak gher letey hain, Allah un sey poochhtey hai : ''merey bandon ko kya kaam kartey huye chhod aaye ho?'' wo kehtey hain : hum unhen teri tareef kartey huye teri buzurgi bayan kartey huye aur tera zikr kartey huye chhod aaye hain, wo kehta hai : ''kya unhoney mujhey dekha hai (ya bin dekhey huye hi meri ibadat aur zikr kiye ja rahey hain)'' wo jawab detey hain : nahin, Allah kehta hai : ''agar wo log mujhey dekh lein to kya surat aur kaifiyat hogi?'' wo jawab detey hain, wo log agar tujhey dekh lein to wo log aur bhi teri tareef karney lagen, teri buzurgi bayan kerengey aur tera zikr badha dengey, wo poochhtey hai : ''wo log kya chahtey aur maangtey hain?'' farishtey kehtey hain : wo log jannat maangtey hain, Allah poochhtey hai ''kya un logon ney jannat dekhi hai?'' wo jawab detey hain : nahin, wo poochhtey hai : ''agar ye dekh lein to un ki kya kaifiyat hogi?'' wo kehtey hain : un ki talab aur un ki hirs aur bhi ziyada badh jaeygi, wo phir poochhtey hai : ''wo log kis chiz sey panah maangtey hain.''  wo kehtey hain : jahannam sey , wo poochhtey hai : ''kya un logon ney jahannam dekh rakhi hai?'' wo kehtey hain : nahin, wo poochhtey hai : ''agar ye log jahannam ko dekh lein to un ki kya kaifiyat hogi?'' wo kehtey hain : agar ye jahannam dekh lein to us sey bahut ziyada door bhaagengey, ziyada khof khaaeyngey aur bahut ziyada us sey panah maangengey, phir Allah kaheyga ''main tumhen gawah bana kar kehta hun ke mainey un sab ki maghfirat kar di hai.''  wo kehtey hain : un mein falan khatakar shakhs bhi hai, unkey paas majlis mein bethney nahin balke kisi zarurat sey aaya tha, (aur beth gaya tha) Allah farmata hai, ''ye aisey (moazziz aur mukarram) log hain ke unka hum nasheeni bhi mehroom nahin reh sakta (hum ney usey bhi bakhsh diya).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai."
3601,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله) kasrat sey padha karo, kyonkey ye jannat key khazanon mein sey eik khazana hai.'' Makhool kehtey hain : jisney kaha : (لا حول wala قوة إلا بالله wala منجا من الله إلا إليه) to Allah Taala us sey sattar tarah key zarar aur nuqsan ko door kar deta hai, jin mein kamtar darjey ka nuksan faqr (aur mohtaji) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : iski sanad muttasil nahin hai, Makhool ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suna hai."
3602,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har Nabi ki eik dua maqbool hoti hai aur mainey apni dua apni ummat ki shafaat key liye mehfooz kar rakhi hai, us dua ka faeyda Insha'allah ummat key har us shakhs ko hasil hoga jisney marney sey pehley Allah key sath kuchh bhi shirk na kiya hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3603,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala kehta hai : main apney bandey key merey sath guman key mutabiq hota hun padhi. , jab wo mujhey yad karta hai to uskey sath hota hun, agar wo mujhey apney dil mein yad karta hai to main bhi usey ji mein yad karta hun aur agar wo mujhey jamaat ( logon ( mein yad karta hai to main usey us sey behtar jamaat mein yad karta hun (yani farishton mein) agar koi mujh sey qarib honey key liye eik baalisht aagey badhta hai to us sey qarib honey key liye main eik haath aagey badhta hun, aur agar koi meri taraf eik haath aagey badhta hai to main uski taraf do haath badhta hun, agar koi meri taraf chal kar aata hai to main uski taraf daud kar aata hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ki tafseer mein Aamash sey marvi hai ke Allah ney ye jo farmaya hai ke ''jo shakhs meri taraf eik baalisht badhta hai main uski taraf eik haath badhta hun'' ,is sey murad ye hai ke main apni rehmat aur maghfirat ka maamla uskey sath karta hun. 3- aur isi tarah baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki tafseer ye ki hai ke us sey murad jab banda meri itaat aur merey maamuraat par amal kar key meri qurbat hasil karna chahta hai to main apni rehmat aur maghfirat ley kar uski taraf tezi sey lapakta hun."
3604,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : (استعيذوا بالله من عذاب جهنم واستعيذوا بالله من عذاب القبر استعيذوا بالله من فتنة المسيح الدجال واستعيذوا بالله من فتنة المحيا والممات) ''Allah sey panah maango jahannam key azab sey , Allah sey panah maango qabr key azab sey , Allah sey panah maango Masih dajjaal key fitney sey aur Allah sey panah maango zindagi aur maut key fitney sey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
